1
00:00:00,285 --> 00:00:02,738
All right. It's finally the last day.

2
00:00:03,748 --> 00:00:06,434
At the end of every
season of "Love Catcher,"

3
00:00:06,459 --> 00:00:09,386
I feel sad because it's over,

4
00:00:09,411 --> 00:00:12,070
but it's also the day when
everyone's identities are revealed.

5
00:00:12,225 --> 00:00:14,590
- I'll feel so light-hearted.
- I can't wait.

6
00:00:14,615 --> 00:00:17,244
Yes, we'll be able to find out
the identities of all eight people.

7
00:00:17,269 --> 00:00:18,619
Oh my goodness.

8
00:00:18,644 --> 00:00:23,724
(Today's Question: Who
are the Love Catchers?)

9
00:00:23,749 --> 00:00:25,364
Not the Money Catchers?

10
00:00:25,389 --> 00:00:28,153
If we find out the Love Catchers,
the others will automatically be...

11
00:00:28,178 --> 00:00:29,653
Money Catchers.

12
00:00:29,678 --> 00:00:34,777
Is there anyone you're certain is a Love
Catcher even before we see the video?

13
00:00:34,802 --> 00:00:37,393
Well, I believe we think
Won-jae is a Love Catcher.

14
00:00:37,418 --> 00:00:41,433
- That's right. I agree.
- Won-jae is a Love Catcher.

15
00:00:41,458 --> 00:00:43,344
- I think Su-won is a Love Catcher.
- Same here.

16
00:00:44,077 --> 00:00:46,743
I think I'm pretty certain that
these two are Love Catchers.

17
00:00:46,768 --> 00:00:50,205
Actually, I was sure that
Ha-neul is a Love Catcher.

18
00:00:50,299 --> 00:00:54,252
However, when Su-won asked
her questions last time, she wouldn't

19
00:00:54,284 --> 00:00:57,821
give him answers but instead
respond with questions of her own.

20
00:00:57,846 --> 00:01:01,195
Why does she keep hiding her feelings?
Does she have something to hide?

21
00:01:01,220 --> 00:01:04,016
So I kind of suspected her
of being a Money Catcher.

22
00:01:04,041 --> 00:01:06,495
What do you think Jae-hyung is?

23
00:01:06,669 --> 00:01:08,027
Like, his identity as a person.

24
00:01:09,158 --> 00:01:10,722
Not whether he's a Love or Money.

25
00:01:10,747 --> 00:01:13,461
If he's a Money Catcher,
he could've fabricated his profile.

26
00:01:13,486 --> 00:01:15,862
He even has a building
that he built himself.

27
00:01:16,103 --> 00:01:18,436
I wonder if that picture is real.

28
00:01:18,461 --> 00:01:21,979
Last week, there was a new love triangle.

29
00:01:22,004 --> 00:01:25,620
- Won-jae, Da-na, and Ji-min.
- That's right.

30
00:01:25,955 --> 00:01:27,407
Do you want to ask him?

31
00:01:27,432 --> 00:01:29,608
If it's okay, you can
spend one or two hours...

32
00:01:29,633 --> 00:01:32,935
(Towards the end, the relationship of
these three people got really tangled up.)

33
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:35,264
- We didn't hear her answer yet.
- Yeah.

34
00:01:35,289 --> 00:01:38,305
- I'm so curious.
- That's what I really want to know.

35
00:01:39,241 --> 00:01:41,142
(Remaining time until the final selection)

36
00:01:41,167 --> 00:01:42,795
There are about seven hours left.

37
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:45,377
Will they spend the rest of the
time with their current dates?

38
00:01:47,019 --> 00:01:48,984
(Amidst fierce competition, Su-won and

39
00:01:49,009 --> 00:01:50,834
Ha-neul are having a peaceful date.)

40
00:01:51,792 --> 00:01:53,863
- Did you tell them we're coming?
- Yes.

41
00:01:53,888 --> 00:01:55,651
- Where?
- Tell them?

42
00:01:56,154 --> 00:01:59,212
Wow, I can't believe
I'm taking you...

43
00:02:00,585 --> 00:02:01,886
to my restaurant.

44
00:02:02,342 --> 00:02:03,619
Oh, really?

45
00:02:04,328 --> 00:02:07,201
- That's right. Ha-neul runs a restaurant.
- What's going on?

46
00:02:07,395 --> 00:02:10,386
My family will be there...

47
00:02:13,672 --> 00:02:15,838
I really get along with parents.

48
00:02:17,658 --> 00:02:20,103
Su-won is really nervous, isn't he?

49
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:26,085
If Ha-neul really is a Money Catcher, that
means her parents are playing along?

50
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:30,208
If she's a Money Catcher, once this is
over, they'll be like, "Hey, that was fun!"

51
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:32,253
Don't worry. I'll be good.

52
00:02:32,882 --> 00:02:34,812
I'm really good at charming mothers.

53
00:02:35,525 --> 00:02:37,377
I've never met a mother
who doesn't like me.

54
00:02:38,078 --> 00:02:39,878
Su-won is really confident.

55
00:02:40,303 --> 00:02:44,670
Does your older sister know your dating
history?

56
00:02:44,695 --> 00:02:46,809
Do you share that
information with each other?

57
00:02:46,834 --> 00:02:48,230
- She knows everything.
- She does?

58
00:02:48,255 --> 00:02:50,246
- Yeah.
- I see.

59
00:02:50,377 --> 00:02:55,528
Then I guess after we
meet, she'll evaluate me.

60
00:02:55,914 --> 00:02:56,914
Totally.

61
00:02:56,939 --> 00:02:58,042
(Nervous)

62
00:02:58,067 --> 00:02:59,267
She probably will.

63
00:03:00,490 --> 00:03:03,135
But my sister likes
good-looking people.

64
00:03:03,722 --> 00:03:04,722
I see.

65
00:03:06,656 --> 00:03:08,346
I hope she'll give me compliments.

66
00:03:09,668 --> 00:03:11,866
They're like a couple
that's about to get married.

67
00:03:11,891 --> 00:03:13,883
It's like they're fixing a
date for their wedding.

68
00:03:13,908 --> 00:03:15,727
They really seem like Love Catchers.

69
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:19,151
- Is this it?
- Yeah.

70
00:03:20,869 --> 00:03:22,893
Now that we're here, I'm
kind of getting nervous.

71
00:03:23,838 --> 00:03:25,435
Oh my goodness.

72
00:03:25,460 --> 00:03:29,858
- There are many wreaths.
- That means the restaurant just opened.

73
00:03:29,883 --> 00:03:32,641
That's why she was described
as a "beautiful rookie owner."

74
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:37,557
- Hello.
- Welcome!

75
00:03:37,648 --> 00:03:39,544
- Hello.
- Hello!

76
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:43,659
How have you been?

77
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:48,054
(Her mom and sister
welcome them with open arms.)

78
00:03:48,812 --> 00:03:50,304
We have to see if they're awkward.

79
00:03:50,329 --> 00:03:52,091
I'm checking if the restaurant is fake.

80
00:03:54,112 --> 00:03:55,405
Come sit here.

81
00:03:57,082 --> 00:04:01,693
- I bought this for you.
- Thank you.

82
00:04:03,565 --> 00:04:06,128
Introducing him to her family must mean...

83
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:09,419
- How have you been?
- Good.

84
00:04:09,444 --> 00:04:11,063
- Did you have fun?
- Yeah.

85
00:04:11,351 --> 00:04:12,351
I see.

86
00:04:13,177 --> 00:04:15,830
- Did you treat my daughter well?
- Yes.

87
00:04:15,855 --> 00:04:18,721
She nearly spent the week with me.

88
00:04:18,746 --> 00:04:19,920
- I see.
- Yes.

89
00:04:20,302 --> 00:04:21,302
(Embarrassed)

90
00:04:22,077 --> 00:04:23,561
What do I do?

91
00:04:24,318 --> 00:04:27,675
- He said he's good with parents.
- Of course he's nervous.

92
00:04:28,108 --> 00:04:29,489
What do you want to eat?

93
00:04:30,377 --> 00:04:32,481
How about hot pot and rice balls?

94
00:04:33,111 --> 00:04:36,170
- Two servings of hot pot and rice balls?
- Yes, please.

95
00:04:36,195 --> 00:04:38,545
- I'll bring those to you.
- I can tell she's beautiful.

96
00:04:38,616 --> 00:04:40,277
- Wait here.
- Okay.

97
00:04:40,302 --> 00:04:41,311
Thank you.

98
00:04:41,336 --> 00:04:43,234
(Ha-neul is uneasier
in front of her family...)

99
00:04:43,259 --> 00:04:45,710
(and Su-won is clearly nervous.)

100
00:04:46,206 --> 00:04:47,406
What do you think?

101
00:04:48,176 --> 00:04:50,145
You said it just opened recently.

102
00:04:51,609 --> 00:04:54,101
It's really clean.

103
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:59,342
There are a lot of plants.
It seems like a plant store.

104
00:05:00,832 --> 00:05:03,237
- Aren't you nervous?
- Nervous? Kind of...

105
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:08,194
- I don't know what to do.
- Me neither.

106
00:05:09,197 --> 00:05:12,126
Why am I so nervous today?

107
00:05:13,032 --> 00:05:15,701
(The hot pot that will save them
from this awkwardness is here.)

108
00:05:15,726 --> 00:05:17,561
- Thank you.
- Hold on.

109
00:05:17,586 --> 00:05:19,500
(Will things get better
if they start eating?)

110
00:05:19,992 --> 00:05:21,829
- Thank you.
- It's hot.

111
00:05:21,854 --> 00:05:23,767
Okay. It's fine.

112
00:05:24,749 --> 00:05:25,749
(Glance)

113
00:05:25,774 --> 00:05:28,714
(Unlike usual, Su-won is really nervous.)

114
00:05:30,230 --> 00:05:32,737
- Can I... sit down for a moment?
- Sure.

115
00:05:34,311 --> 00:05:36,199
Su-won's getting paler and paler.

116
00:05:36,224 --> 00:05:38,577
Moms can see right through you.

117
00:05:38,602 --> 00:05:41,735
- She can tell if he's Love or Money.
- Right.

118
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:44,947
(How will her mom see Su-won?)

119
00:05:45,666 --> 00:05:47,324
- It's hot, huh?
- How was it?

120
00:05:48,646 --> 00:05:49,646
How was it?

121
00:05:50,606 --> 00:05:54,037
- We... had a good time.
We spent the week together. - Really?

122
00:05:54,062 --> 00:05:55,778
We were at the house together,

123
00:05:56,088 --> 00:05:58,523
and it felt like...

124
00:05:59,008 --> 00:06:01,675
Ha-neul and I knew each other for years.

125
00:06:01,833 --> 00:06:02,833
I see.

126
00:06:04,048 --> 00:06:06,058
You must like Ha-neul.

127
00:06:06,886 --> 00:06:09,045
Fortunately, she responded to my feelings.

128
00:06:09,291 --> 00:06:10,291
I see.

129
00:06:10,316 --> 00:06:12,056
(Embarrassed)

130
00:06:12,081 --> 00:06:19,466
Ha-neul seems bright and down-to-earth,

131
00:06:19,491 --> 00:06:22,463
but she's very soft-hearted,
and she cries easily.

132
00:06:23,159 --> 00:06:27,936
She's the youngest, so she's very lovable.

133
00:06:27,961 --> 00:06:28,961
Right.

134
00:06:29,188 --> 00:06:34,642
I like down-to-earth people.

135
00:06:34,667 --> 00:06:36,526
Then that's perfect.

136
00:06:37,666 --> 00:06:40,237
- That's wonderful.
- Yes.

137
00:06:40,262 --> 00:06:42,962
Doesn't it seem like she approves of him?

138
00:06:43,736 --> 00:06:46,338
- I hope it works out.
- Thank you.

139
00:06:46,452 --> 00:06:47,896
She must like him.

140
00:06:48,558 --> 00:06:50,390
- Enjoy.
- Thanks.

141
00:06:50,415 --> 00:06:52,202
What do you think about him, Mom?

142
00:06:52,227 --> 00:06:55,419
He's really handsome.

143
00:06:56,986 --> 00:07:01,051
He seems like a very good-natured person.

144
00:07:01,076 --> 00:07:02,343
- Oh, I do?
- Yes.

145
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:06,113
- You seem like someone with a
good heart, so I like you. - Thank you.

146
00:07:07,792 --> 00:07:10,443
I'll make an effort so
that you will like me more.

147
00:07:10,468 --> 00:07:13,446
- Yes, please do that.
- I will.

148
00:07:14,013 --> 00:07:16,346
- Enjoy.
- Thank you.

149
00:07:16,715 --> 00:07:19,446
- She gave me some compliments.
- Yeah, you made it.

150
00:07:20,970 --> 00:07:22,502
(Relieved)

151
00:07:23,548 --> 00:07:27,825
Her mother probably saw a lot
of things within that short time.

152
00:07:28,020 --> 00:07:29,583
I'm curious what she thought.

153
00:07:29,608 --> 00:07:30,608
Hang on.

154
00:07:31,157 --> 00:07:32,659
Where... Where are you going?

155
00:07:33,264 --> 00:07:34,525
To get some drinks.

156
00:07:34,550 --> 00:07:37,788
(Ha-neul leaves for a bit, and
Su-won is left all alone.)

157
00:07:38,507 --> 00:07:39,997
(Rice ball)

158
00:07:41,455 --> 00:07:43,581
He looks uneasy. He
looks nervous and uneasy.

159
00:07:45,197 --> 00:07:47,554
If you think he's okay...

160
00:07:49,797 --> 00:07:51,599
- bring us Sprite.
- Okay.

161
00:07:51,861 --> 00:07:55,260
If you don't think he's
okay, bring us Fanta.

162
00:07:55,563 --> 00:07:57,443
- If I don't like him?
- Yeah.

163
00:07:59,623 --> 00:08:02,886
(The sisters are coming up
with a secret plan in the corner.)

164
00:08:03,699 --> 00:08:05,270
Do you like him?

165
00:08:07,718 --> 00:08:09,147
(Ha-neul answers honestly.)

166
00:08:10,764 --> 00:08:14,899
If she didn't, she wouldn't be
able to bring him to her restaurant.

167
00:08:16,005 --> 00:08:18,411
(Ha-neul comes back.)

168
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:20,915
(Su-won gives her the
rice balls he rolled himself.)

169
00:08:24,887 --> 00:08:27,753
Can you give me some w-w-water?

170
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:30,019
Oh no. He's shaking.

171
00:08:30,044 --> 00:08:32,434
(Seems like he's still nervous.)

172
00:08:33,811 --> 00:08:35,422
His throat is burning.

173
00:08:36,807 --> 00:08:38,616
(So cute.)

174
00:08:39,213 --> 00:08:41,396
(At last, Ha-neul's sister
appears with the drinks.)

175
00:08:41,421 --> 00:08:43,240
(Please let it be Sprite...!)

176
00:08:43,858 --> 00:08:47,201
(Does she like Su-won?)

177
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:51,429
(2nd Evaluation by
Ha-neul's sister: Approved)

178
00:08:51,454 --> 00:08:52,454
Sprite!

179
00:08:53,724 --> 00:08:55,894
(Trying to control her expression)

180
00:08:56,755 --> 00:08:58,780
- This is hot. Hold on.
- Okay.

181
00:09:00,976 --> 00:09:04,547
(Finally, the hefty clam hot pot is ready.)

182
00:09:04,894 --> 00:09:07,249
If it weren't for COVID-19, we
could've eaten dinner there.

183
00:09:07,274 --> 00:09:09,736
What was that place
called? Clam Gangster Lab?

184
00:09:09,761 --> 00:09:11,214
"C.G.L."

185
00:09:11,380 --> 00:09:12,380
What?

186
00:09:13,099 --> 00:09:15,694
I was just abbreviating it.

187
00:09:16,930 --> 00:09:18,413
Did you have a fun date?

188
00:09:19,905 --> 00:09:20,905
Yes.

189
00:09:21,744 --> 00:09:24,196
I mostly went on dates with Su-won.

190
00:09:24,221 --> 00:09:25,221
Really?

191
00:09:25,564 --> 00:09:27,579
- We danced together, too.
- What kind of dance?

192
00:09:28,008 --> 00:09:30,287
It was like a sports dance.

193
00:09:30,312 --> 00:09:34,737
We learned it for about two to
three hours and got assessed.

194
00:09:34,769 --> 00:09:36,769
Assessed? What's your ranking?

195
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:38,878
- We didn't win.
- We didn't get first place,

196
00:09:39,056 --> 00:09:41,571
but I think we beat
everyone in terms of looks.

197
00:09:42,472 --> 00:09:45,654
Even though he's nervous,
he said that very clearly.

198
00:09:46,866 --> 00:09:50,771
I think so. You're handsome, too.

199
00:09:52,014 --> 00:09:54,411
- He's handsome, right?
- Yeah, he's really good-looking.

200
00:09:54,436 --> 00:09:56,548
See? I knew my sister would like you.

201
00:09:57,130 --> 00:09:59,058
I told him you like handsome guys.

202
00:10:02,508 --> 00:10:04,032
Do you like to drink?

203
00:10:04,381 --> 00:10:06,970
Ha-neul doesn't drink.

204
00:10:07,228 --> 00:10:10,458
I'm not that good of a drinker either.

205
00:10:11,017 --> 00:10:13,185
You two have a lot of things in common.

206
00:10:13,537 --> 00:10:14,997
Yes, I think so.

207
00:10:15,886 --> 00:10:17,528
(Nod)

208
00:10:18,264 --> 00:10:19,300
Enjoy.

209
00:10:19,325 --> 00:10:22,472
It might seem like she's carelessly
asking questions while cutting the food...

210
00:10:22,983 --> 00:10:24,673
But each of those are barriers.

211
00:10:26,130 --> 00:10:28,717
I can't believe we're having
the last date at my restaurant.

212
00:10:29,173 --> 00:10:33,913
- But I think it's a meaningful location.
- Yeah, to me it is.

213
00:10:35,536 --> 00:10:39,108
It's better than the common
places other couples go to.

214
00:10:40,179 --> 00:10:41,845
I get to see your family.

215
00:10:43,831 --> 00:10:46,457
I think it's great.

216
00:10:47,174 --> 00:10:49,913
It kind of feels...

217
00:10:50,403 --> 00:10:51,693
like I'm naked.

218
00:10:52,164 --> 00:10:54,505
It feels like I'm showing you my true self.

219
00:10:54,530 --> 00:10:56,944
It's not easy to introduce
your family members.

220
00:10:57,862 --> 00:10:59,671
Right. That's a big deal.

221
00:11:00,619 --> 00:11:04,714
We have to make our final
selection when we go back.

222
00:11:04,857 --> 00:11:05,857
Right.

223
00:11:07,531 --> 00:11:09,428
Don't you feel any pressure?

224
00:11:10,073 --> 00:11:11,073
Even before...

225
00:11:13,033 --> 00:11:14,767
we went on this last date today...

226
00:11:16,024 --> 00:11:18,333
I already made up my mind.

227
00:11:20,108 --> 00:11:24,489
I didn't ask you on a date
today to check your feelings.

228
00:11:25,907 --> 00:11:30,288
I just wanted to spend
time with you today, too.

229
00:11:30,698 --> 00:11:32,729
Oh my god. Woohoo!

230
00:11:34,050 --> 00:11:35,376
I could see that...

231
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:41,228
you wanted to introduce me to your family.

232
00:11:43,109 --> 00:11:45,926
So it gave me conviction.

233
00:11:46,126 --> 00:11:47,944
I think he was touched.

234
00:11:47,969 --> 00:11:50,932
(He honestly shares
his thoughts as always.)

235
00:11:50,957 --> 00:11:52,157
That's how I feel.

236
00:11:54,477 --> 00:11:55,477
What about you?

237
00:11:56,217 --> 00:12:00,383
I think the biggest
thing I'm attracted to is

238
00:12:01,086 --> 00:12:05,032
when the guy constantly
expresses his feelings for me.

239
00:12:05,199 --> 00:12:06,199
I see.

240
00:12:07,658 --> 00:12:09,591
From the first day until now,

241
00:12:10,198 --> 00:12:13,180
I didn't feel have stronger
feelings for anyone...

242
00:12:14,584 --> 00:12:16,957
than you.

243
00:12:17,715 --> 00:12:25,309
It feels like we've
always known each other.

244
00:12:25,603 --> 00:12:27,979
Yeah. It was comfortable
ever since the beginning.

245
00:12:28,004 --> 00:12:30,004
Our conversations just flowed.

246
00:12:30,991 --> 00:12:34,364
Right. They gave off couple
vibes ever since the beginning.

247
00:12:35,116 --> 00:12:40,063
I didn't have a bad first
impression of her family.

248
00:12:40,208 --> 00:12:43,588
Later on, if Ha-neul and I
become a true couple and I

249
00:12:43,954 --> 00:12:46,942
see her family again, I
won't get on their wrong side.

250
00:12:47,992 --> 00:12:50,248
Su-won must have felt awkward,

251
00:12:50,973 --> 00:12:53,905
but he spoke very kindly
and tried really hard to get

252
00:12:53,930 --> 00:12:56,753
along with my family, so
I felt really grateful.

253
00:12:57,575 --> 00:13:00,877
- This couple is already...
- They'll pick each other.

254
00:13:00,902 --> 00:13:03,293
At this rate, they're both Love Catchers.

255
00:13:03,724 --> 00:13:06,994
- If they're not...
- There's no room for doubt.

256
00:13:07,285 --> 00:13:12,612
(Remaining time until the final selection)

257
00:13:12,885 --> 00:13:15,989
- I feel like you don't drink that much.
- Yeah, about once a week?

258
00:13:16,014 --> 00:13:17,475
- I see.
- What about you?

259
00:13:19,193 --> 00:13:21,161
Four days a week?

260
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,817
- Should we...?
- Hmm?

261
00:13:26,321 --> 00:13:29,921
Once the sun sets a little,
should we go grab a drink?

262
00:13:32,032 --> 00:13:33,765
Should we go grab a drink?

263
00:13:34,643 --> 00:13:35,643
Really?

264
00:13:36,454 --> 00:13:38,155
(Da-Na can't answer right away.)

265
00:13:38,180 --> 00:13:41,745
They're getting to know each other.

266
00:13:41,770 --> 00:13:44,114
So I think they'll be
curious about each other.

267
00:13:44,783 --> 00:13:47,117
(Meanwhile, at Love Mansion...)

268
00:13:47,142 --> 00:13:51,477
(Won-jae is endlessly waiting for Da-Na.)

269
00:13:52,932 --> 00:13:55,887
(He's moving.)

270
00:13:57,535 --> 00:13:59,193
(Rummage)

271
00:14:02,504 --> 00:14:05,817
(Where is he doing?)

272
00:14:06,982 --> 00:14:08,838
Won-jae changed his clothes first.

273
00:14:09,397 --> 00:14:12,460
(Won-jae is ready to go out,
and Da-Na is still thinking.)

274
00:14:13,265 --> 00:14:15,489
(Hesitate)

275
00:14:17,134 --> 00:14:19,324
- Do you have plans tonight?
- Yeah.

276
00:14:20,302 --> 00:14:22,686
Oh, really? Okay then.
What time do you have to be there by?

277
00:14:22,711 --> 00:14:25,379
I think I need to reply to him now.

278
00:14:25,404 --> 00:14:28,326
Oh, really? So you
haven't decided the time yet.

279
00:14:28,351 --> 00:14:29,351
Yeah.

280
00:14:30,207 --> 00:14:32,990
(They're together now,
but she'll be leaving soon.)

281
00:14:33,607 --> 00:14:37,081
(And he'll have to watch that happen.)

282
00:14:40,485 --> 00:14:42,279
It feels really strange.

283
00:14:43,266 --> 00:14:45,663
- Of course it does.
- It's really strange.

284
00:14:46,203 --> 00:14:48,023
The one you like is
contacting someone else.

285
00:14:48,048 --> 00:14:49,048
(Thinking)

286
00:14:50,416 --> 00:14:53,188
Do you want to ask him...

287
00:14:56,330 --> 00:14:57,979
what time you're going to hang out?

288
00:14:58,004 --> 00:15:00,338
If it's okay, you can
spend one or two hours...

289
00:15:00,363 --> 00:15:01,363
Oh.

290
00:15:02,777 --> 00:15:04,153
He's not giving up.

291
00:15:05,705 --> 00:15:07,105
I was really nervous.

292
00:15:07,681 --> 00:15:12,105
Her answer was going to
depend on who she likes more.

293
00:15:12,776 --> 00:15:15,376
If she rejects me, then it's game over.

294
00:15:18,948 --> 00:15:20,638
He changed his clothes first.

295
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:23,705
(Thinking)

296
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:27,316
(Ji-min? Won-jae?)

297
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:32,229
(Who will Da-Na choose?)

298
00:15:32,254 --> 00:15:34,597
Gosh, it must be so hard for her.

299
00:15:36,498 --> 00:15:40,835
(Remaining time until the final selection)

300
00:15:40,860 --> 00:15:42,621
I thought I was going
to have a heart attack.

301
00:15:42,646 --> 00:15:47,196
- The sound of the ticking clock...
- It's like Won-jae's nervous heart.

302
00:15:47,221 --> 00:15:49,606
It really expresses that.

303
00:15:50,942 --> 00:15:52,910
He's just holding onto his cell phone.

304
00:15:52,935 --> 00:15:54,166
(Nervous)

305
00:15:54,464 --> 00:15:56,891
(And Ji-min has moved locations.)

306
00:15:56,916 --> 00:15:58,249
Oh, what's going on?

307
00:15:58,471 --> 00:15:59,538
What's going on?

308
00:15:59,841 --> 00:16:00,841
What's that?

309
00:16:01,443 --> 00:16:03,261
They went to drink?

310
00:16:03,543 --> 00:16:04,765
Did he go there alone?

311
00:16:04,790 --> 00:16:07,091
Are there one or two plates?

312
00:16:07,116 --> 00:16:08,515
There's something
in front of him.

313
00:16:08,540 --> 00:16:11,056
- No, there isn't.
- There's no glass there.

314
00:16:11,176 --> 00:16:14,789
He went to drink alone? What's going on?
That's so lonely.

315
00:16:16,809 --> 00:16:18,547
(Sigh)

316
00:16:19,259 --> 00:16:23,957
(A love triangle with one woman...
What is the fate of the two men?)

317
00:16:24,383 --> 00:16:25,668
What happened?

318
00:16:25,803 --> 00:16:28,075
What's going on? Who did
she go to? What happened?

319
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:29,833
Hurry!

320
00:16:30,189 --> 00:16:31,791
(Won-jae?)

321
00:16:31,816 --> 00:16:33,453
(Ji-min?)

322
00:16:33,682 --> 00:16:37,574
(Da-Na has chosen Ji-min.)

323
00:16:37,599 --> 00:16:40,969
See! Oh no!

324
00:16:41,947 --> 00:16:42,947
Oh no.

325
00:16:43,909 --> 00:16:45,608
Oh my god. This is actually happening?

326
00:16:45,633 --> 00:16:47,404
Ji-min did it.

327
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:50,776
- All the food's here?
- They brought it just now.

328
00:16:52,849 --> 00:16:55,087
What? Did you peel the peas?

329
00:16:56,182 --> 00:16:58,613
(10 minutes ago)

330
00:16:59,683 --> 00:17:03,349
(The sound of the phone
ringing is filling up the room.)

331
00:17:03,374 --> 00:17:05,781
We thought she'd go to Won-jae.

332
00:17:06,466 --> 00:17:08,546
He probably thought they
were going to meet up.

333
00:17:08,571 --> 00:17:10,160
- Hello?
- Hello?

334
00:17:10,342 --> 00:17:12,622
Hey. I called late, didn't I?

335
00:17:13,438 --> 00:17:16,014
- What are you doing?
- Um, right now...

336
00:17:16,819 --> 00:17:23,187
Ji-min said he made
reservations at an Izakaya.

337
00:17:23,212 --> 00:17:24,992
- Okay.
- So I just got here.

338
00:17:25,017 --> 00:17:27,945
- I can't watch!
- I don't want to hear it.

339
00:17:29,106 --> 00:17:32,680
(Does he have to wait longer?)

340
00:17:33,139 --> 00:17:36,107
Where is that restaurant?

341
00:17:36,633 --> 00:17:38,323
- Samseong.
- Samseong?

342
00:17:38,596 --> 00:17:39,850
Yes, that's right.

343
00:17:40,329 --> 00:17:44,352
Then when you're done,

344
00:17:45,685 --> 00:17:49,255
can you just stay there?
I'll go to you when you're ready.

345
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:51,184
Oh, you will?

346
00:17:52,492 --> 00:17:56,359
This is hard. She's on a date, but
she also made a promise with Won-jae.

347
00:17:59,150 --> 00:18:04,641
(Da-Na is standing at a
crossroads of decisions again.)

348
00:18:05,339 --> 00:18:07,505
- Won-jae.
- Yeah?

349
00:18:09,002 --> 00:18:12,002
I'll make sure to go to you by 8 o'clock.

350
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:16,108
Let's eat when I get there.

351
00:18:16,809 --> 00:18:17,943
His expression...

352
00:18:18,494 --> 00:18:20,161
Aren't you eating with him?

353
00:18:21,037 --> 00:18:22,766
Hmm, I won't eat a lot.

354
00:18:23,484 --> 00:18:24,849
Is that okay?

355
00:18:26,027 --> 00:18:27,621
Yeah, alright.

356
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:31,562
What do I do? I can't
watch this. It's too sad.

357
00:18:31,587 --> 00:18:34,429
I can't watch this! Oh dear!

358
00:18:35,291 --> 00:18:38,530
Okay. I'm sorry I couldn't keep my promise.

359
00:18:39,628 --> 00:18:40,628
No, it's fine.

360
00:18:41,627 --> 00:18:44,774
- Okay, see you later.
- I feel like he's gonna cry!

361
00:18:45,006 --> 00:18:49,157
He's angry and hurt.

362
00:18:49,182 --> 00:18:51,797
(Da-Na pushed back the date with Won-jae.)

363
00:18:53,213 --> 00:18:56,641
(He has to wait again.)

364
00:18:57,868 --> 00:19:01,958
(Did Da-na's heart go to Ji-min?)

365
00:19:05,791 --> 00:19:08,338
(Mixed feelings)

366
00:19:09,876 --> 00:19:14,338
It's unfortunate. It could've been better
if he had gone on a date with her first.

367
00:19:14,363 --> 00:19:18,299
He might have wanted to
end the day with her, but...

368
00:19:18,324 --> 00:19:21,400
We saw that Ji-min and
Da-na's date went so well.

369
00:19:21,425 --> 00:19:23,156
It went well.

370
00:19:25,487 --> 00:19:27,416
- It's really good, right?
- Yeah.

371
00:19:28,849 --> 00:19:31,315
- Shall we have a drink?
- Shall we?

372
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:33,168
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

373
00:19:33,193 --> 00:19:36,193
(Their second date started with drinks.)

374
00:19:39,303 --> 00:19:41,390
- Just drink a little bit.
- Why?

375
00:19:41,415 --> 00:19:42,789
So that I can drink more.

376
00:19:43,177 --> 00:19:44,370
(Kidding)

377
00:19:46,016 --> 00:19:48,127
It's too precious. Don't drink a lot.

378
00:19:48,894 --> 00:19:50,234
- Are you tying your hair?
- Yeah.

379
00:19:50,259 --> 00:19:53,291
I usually wear my hair up.

380
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:56,180
You look pretty with your hair up
and some loose hair down.

381
00:19:57,107 --> 00:20:00,195
She definitely seems comfortable with him.

382
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:02,706
Isn't there anyone you
want to talk more with?

383
00:20:05,734 --> 00:20:07,473
(Thinking)

384
00:20:08,522 --> 00:20:09,761
(Curious)

385
00:20:10,392 --> 00:20:12,939
I think I had the most fun
when we talked in the car.

386
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:15,807
It was so much fun.

387
00:20:16,301 --> 00:20:18,453
Our conversation kept flowing.

388
00:20:19,191 --> 00:20:20,914
I enjoyed it, too.

389
00:20:22,547 --> 00:20:25,024
That was really cute. I
should do that next time.

390
00:20:25,392 --> 00:20:27,225
When you slide down that wall.

391
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:29,273
Wouldn't it be charming
if I just slid right down

392
00:20:29,298 --> 00:20:31,401
to the floor and crawled
out through the other side?

393
00:20:31,426 --> 00:20:33,278
(That's hilarious!)

394
00:20:34,528 --> 00:20:37,283
In that aspect, I'm
grateful to you because...

395
00:20:37,794 --> 00:20:41,325
you enjoy the time we spend together.

396
00:20:41,853 --> 00:20:43,297
It's a lot of fun.

397
00:20:43,812 --> 00:20:44,812
(Really?)

398
00:20:44,837 --> 00:20:45,837
It's all great.

399
00:20:47,747 --> 00:20:49,710
While staying at
Love Mansion, I really

400
00:20:49,735 --> 00:20:52,735
liked seeing your bright
and confident sides.

401
00:20:56,654 --> 00:20:59,988
Da-Na seems happy but unsure.

402
00:21:00,013 --> 00:21:02,888
(Ji-min is actively
expressing his feelings.)

403
00:21:04,675 --> 00:21:08,091
(And then there's silence.)

404
00:21:09,121 --> 00:21:10,854
Why is there so little time?

405
00:21:13,951 --> 00:21:16,379
Would things have been
different if there was more time?

406
00:21:18,256 --> 00:21:21,885
I don't know about you, but I
observe people for a long time.

407
00:21:22,627 --> 00:21:25,483
I'm supposed to look at every aspect.

408
00:21:27,743 --> 00:21:30,179
There really wasn't enough
time to get to know you.

409
00:21:31,516 --> 00:21:32,928
I was a bit late, wasn't I?

410
00:21:34,512 --> 00:21:36,702
It's difficult. There's limited time.

411
00:21:36,727 --> 00:21:39,586
(They're more affectionate because
there's not that much time left.)

412
00:21:43,733 --> 00:21:45,558
Why is she crying?

413
00:21:45,583 --> 00:21:47,619
I think it would have been really hard.

414
00:21:47,826 --> 00:21:49,381
Why are you crying?

415
00:21:52,730 --> 00:21:54,007
Why are you crying?

416
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:57,685
She has to keep making decisions,
and the guys are waiting for her.

417
00:22:00,095 --> 00:22:04,492
We've never had time to share things.

418
00:22:04,886 --> 00:22:10,131
We only talked briefly.

419
00:22:10,725 --> 00:22:12,685
We didn't spend time together.

420
00:22:16,205 --> 00:22:17,641
It is unfortunate.

421
00:22:20,114 --> 00:22:24,442
(There was limited time,
and their timing was off.)

422
00:22:24,467 --> 00:22:26,056
Why are you crying so much?

423
00:22:33,335 --> 00:22:35,946
Why am I so indecisive?

424
00:22:38,570 --> 00:22:41,778
- Goodness.
- I think I know how she feels.

425
00:22:44,126 --> 00:22:45,673
First off,

426
00:22:47,221 --> 00:22:49,812
it's not like only one person
showed interest in me.

427
00:22:50,609 --> 00:22:51,918
It feels like...

428
00:22:53,682 --> 00:22:55,786
What do you think?
Are you glad you came out?

429
00:22:56,821 --> 00:22:57,821
I'm glad.

430
00:23:00,397 --> 00:23:04,801
Honestly, whether you're a Love Catcher
or a Money Catcher doesn't matter to me.

431
00:23:06,340 --> 00:23:09,626
I'm grateful to you because you
enjoy the time we spend together.

432
00:23:10,157 --> 00:23:11,610
It's a lot of fun.

433
00:23:13,903 --> 00:23:16,133
I'm really grateful
for their hearts, but...

434
00:23:21,125 --> 00:23:23,125
I don't know what I should do.

435
00:23:27,259 --> 00:23:29,830
They didn't really have a
chance to talk or hang out,

436
00:23:30,441 --> 00:23:33,953
but their conversations
are smooth and comfortable.

437
00:23:34,839 --> 00:23:39,013
But she can't ignore Won-jae either.

438
00:23:43,431 --> 00:23:48,205
(The regret of being one step
late makes his eyes tear up as well.)

439
00:23:56,266 --> 00:24:00,837
(What will they choose?)

440
00:24:01,518 --> 00:24:03,184
If you're a Money Catcher,

441
00:24:04,343 --> 00:24:06,329
choose me to be safe, okay?

442
00:24:08,001 --> 00:24:09,001
Oh my gosh.

443
00:24:09,026 --> 00:24:12,280
Oh my god! This is like a movie!

444
00:24:12,607 --> 00:24:14,400
What? I just got goosebumps.

445
00:24:14,425 --> 00:24:16,507
The hair on the back of my neck stood up.

446
00:24:16,532 --> 00:24:18,758
- Oh my goodness.
- What is he saying?

447
00:24:18,783 --> 00:24:22,250
He's even crying. It's so sorrowful
and desperate. What do we do?

448
00:24:22,275 --> 00:24:24,093
He's being sincere.

449
00:24:26,027 --> 00:24:27,761
If you're a Money Catcher,

450
00:24:28,884 --> 00:24:30,990
choose me to be safe, okay?

451
00:24:34,964 --> 00:24:35,964
Okay?

452
00:24:38,556 --> 00:24:40,477
What? He's getting that emotional?

453
00:24:41,356 --> 00:24:45,397
(Are his overflowing
feelings flowing as tears?)

454
00:24:46,656 --> 00:24:48,715
(Emotional synchronization)

455
00:24:48,938 --> 00:24:50,702
Oh no.

456
00:24:54,962 --> 00:24:58,558
(Are we Love Catchers?)

457
00:24:59,656 --> 00:25:02,079
(Remaining time until the final selection)

458
00:25:02,104 --> 00:25:04,041
I wish time would go by slowly.

459
00:25:10,043 --> 00:25:12,741
I'm glad we made centerpieces.
We get to keep them like a memento.

460
00:25:13,498 --> 00:25:15,435
We should show these off.

461
00:25:15,556 --> 00:25:18,548
We went early in the morning.
We have to show them off.

462
00:25:19,972 --> 00:25:21,449
I wonder if anyone's here.

463
00:25:24,469 --> 00:25:27,152
- Change and get some rest.
- Okay.

464
00:25:27,488 --> 00:25:28,488
Here.

465
00:25:31,056 --> 00:25:34,256
- Oh, Won-jae.
- He keeps looking at his phone.

466
00:25:35,387 --> 00:25:36,990
- Did you go on a date?
- What?

467
00:25:37,529 --> 00:25:40,015
Why would you ask? Don't ask him that!

468
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,335
He doesn't know.

469
00:25:41,965 --> 00:25:44,004
- Did you go on a date?
- What?

470
00:25:44,029 --> 00:25:45,626
(Su-won has no idea what's going on.)

471
00:25:46,166 --> 00:25:47,432
You didn't?

472
00:25:49,116 --> 00:25:50,298
No way.

473
00:25:52,952 --> 00:25:54,960
You were just here the whole time?

474
00:25:57,482 --> 00:25:58,682
That's unexpected.

475
00:25:58,921 --> 00:26:00,476
Su-won, just go inside.

476
00:26:01,294 --> 00:26:03,277
Don't ask him anymore questions.

477
00:26:05,855 --> 00:26:06,855
Yeo-min!

478
00:26:07,731 --> 00:26:09,135
Yeo-min and Won-jae...

479
00:26:09,724 --> 00:26:11,025
What's wrong?

480
00:26:11,050 --> 00:26:12,933
- It's my fault.
- What's wrong?

481
00:26:14,043 --> 00:26:15,928
This whole thing is annoying.

482
00:26:15,953 --> 00:26:18,557
(At the sight of Ha-neul,
she's flooded with sadness.)

483
00:26:18,797 --> 00:26:20,424
My small decision...

484
00:26:22,197 --> 00:26:25,341
- I seriously...
- No one knew it would turn out like this.

485
00:26:26,115 --> 00:26:28,329
I couldn't even go on a date with him.

486
00:26:30,818 --> 00:26:32,351
Won-jae, what happened?

487
00:26:32,972 --> 00:26:37,061
Yesterday, Yeo-min
texted me asking if we can

488
00:26:38,316 --> 00:26:40,453
see each other at lunch and talk.

489
00:26:41,035 --> 00:26:44,239
I told her, "I'm sorry. I
already made plans, so I don't

490
00:26:44,264 --> 00:26:47,242
think I can hang out with
you. Let's just talk here."

491
00:26:47,439 --> 00:26:49,106
He didn't make any plans.

492
00:26:49,569 --> 00:26:54,196
I didn't know they were
going to leave this place.

493
00:26:54,228 --> 00:26:56,199
I thought they were
going to talk here like me.

494
00:26:56,224 --> 00:26:57,431
I see.

495
00:26:58,110 --> 00:26:59,768
I thought she was
going to come back soon.

496
00:27:00,070 --> 00:27:02,627
But when I realized that wasn't the case...

497
00:27:03,906 --> 00:27:08,015
I felt so bad that I couldn't
look at Yeo-min's face.

498
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,040
I get it.

499
00:27:09,470 --> 00:27:12,398
I thought I was going mad in here.

500
00:27:12,911 --> 00:27:14,466
I thought...

501
00:27:15,427 --> 00:27:17,159
Da-Na was interested in you.

502
00:27:17,184 --> 00:27:18,517
That's how I saw it.

503
00:27:19,013 --> 00:27:24,776
You probably don't have to worry so much
just because she went on a date with him.

504
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:28,940
Of course, I'm sure that's not how
you feel since she's with him right now.

505
00:27:29,969 --> 00:27:31,485
All I can tell you...

506
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:36,782
is that from Da-na's perspective,
it's right for her to spend time...

507
00:27:38,476 --> 00:27:39,674
with different guys.

508
00:27:39,699 --> 00:27:41,081
Just keep that in mind.

509
00:27:41,542 --> 00:27:44,808
When she gets here,
you can talk it out with her.

510
00:27:46,502 --> 00:27:50,344
The best thing you can
do is try to win her heart.

511
00:27:52,508 --> 00:27:55,976
(Remaining time until the final selection)

512
00:27:56,862 --> 00:27:58,964
- They're here.
- Oh, Ji-min.

513
00:27:59,189 --> 00:28:00,586
I had a great time.

514
00:28:00,706 --> 00:28:02,430
Me, too. I had fun.

515
00:28:02,455 --> 00:28:03,522
Yeah, same here.

516
00:28:04,702 --> 00:28:06,250
- Go in.
- Okay.

517
00:28:09,057 --> 00:28:12,922
(For some reason, Ji-min's
footsteps seem light.)

518
00:28:15,370 --> 00:28:16,370
(Glance)

519
00:28:16,629 --> 00:28:18,739
(Won-jae fell asleep while waiting.)

520
00:28:18,764 --> 00:28:21,473
- That's so sad!
- He's going to get a cramp in his neck.

521
00:28:21,498 --> 00:28:23,864
- Oh no.
- Oh gosh. What's going on?

522
00:28:24,450 --> 00:28:27,645
(His desperate wait can be felt from
the way he couldn't even lie down.)

523
00:28:28,647 --> 00:28:29,647
(Toss)

524
00:28:32,140 --> 00:28:35,741
(Won-jae fell into such a deep sleep that
he doesn't even realize Ji-min is back.)

525
00:28:37,794 --> 00:28:39,349
Hey!

526
00:28:39,374 --> 00:28:41,374
I'm back.

527
00:28:41,875 --> 00:28:43,219
Your cheeks are flushed.

528
00:28:44,139 --> 00:28:45,273
Where did you go?

529
00:28:46,620 --> 00:28:48,802
- Bongeunsa.
- She's really flushed.

530
00:28:49,654 --> 00:28:50,980
Bongeunsa? Where else?

531
00:28:51,666 --> 00:28:56,269
We looked around Bongeunsa and
went to drink at an Izakaya nearby.

532
00:28:57,457 --> 00:29:00,910
But why didn't you come back early?

533
00:29:00,935 --> 00:29:02,817
Weren't you going to go
on a date with Won-jae?

534
00:29:02,841 --> 00:29:05,089
It seemed like he's been waiting for you.

535
00:29:06,810 --> 00:29:10,166
It'd be a good idea for you to
call Won-jae and talk to him a bit.

536
00:29:11,552 --> 00:29:13,051
They must've been curious about that.

537
00:29:16,229 --> 00:29:17,466
He woke up.

538
00:29:18,933 --> 00:29:21,528
- He keeps checking his phone.
- It's so hard.

539
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:27,501
(There's no word from Da-Na yet...)

540
00:29:29,180 --> 00:29:30,180
He spots him.

541
00:29:30,325 --> 00:29:31,698
Oh, he's here.

542
00:29:32,013 --> 00:29:34,294
I just woke up, but it
seemed like she was back.

543
00:29:34,319 --> 00:29:36,694
He sees that Ji-min is back.

544
00:29:36,719 --> 00:29:40,641
Da-Na came back, but
she didn't contact him yet.

545
00:29:42,545 --> 00:29:46,838
(Eventually, he calls her first.)

546
00:29:48,939 --> 00:29:51,853
(Da-Na isn't picking up.)

547
00:29:51,878 --> 00:29:55,211
I don't think it's a bad idea
for you to go there directly.

548
00:29:55,867 --> 00:29:58,661
Wouldn't that be better?
I think it is.

549
00:29:59,921 --> 00:30:01,500
There are only two hours left.

550
00:30:02,899 --> 00:30:08,527
(There's no time to waste.
Won-jae goes to Da-Na first.)

551
00:30:12,474 --> 00:30:15,513
(Da-Na just happens to be with Yeo-min.)

552
00:30:16,905 --> 00:30:19,740
Hold on. Just give me five
minutes. No, three minutes.

553
00:30:22,887 --> 00:30:25,578
(Yeo-min puts on a brave smile.)

554
00:30:26,302 --> 00:30:28,168
Go on.

555
00:30:28,193 --> 00:30:30,639
I want to give Yeo-min a hug.

556
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,746
Gosh, my heart breaks.

557
00:30:33,773 --> 00:30:35,257
Go on.

558
00:30:37,719 --> 00:30:41,253
(It's a game where the one
who loves more will lose.)

559
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,392
(Stumble)

560
00:30:45,428 --> 00:30:48,682
This one day is more
intense than the first six days.

561
00:30:48,707 --> 00:30:50,607
Right. It all just
comes crashing down.

562
00:30:50,632 --> 00:30:53,165
This one last day of
the final selection is...

563
00:30:53,459 --> 00:30:56,294
It's like a roller coaster.
It's full of twists.

564
00:30:56,751 --> 00:31:00,323
(The moon is oblivious to his
heartbreak and shines brightly.)

565
00:31:01,396 --> 00:31:04,614
(It's almost time for the final selection.)

566
00:31:05,832 --> 00:31:10,173
(And these two don't have much time left.)

567
00:31:11,727 --> 00:31:15,021
(Won-jae waited all day for
her, but he's not saying anything.)

568
00:31:15,667 --> 00:31:17,494
(Peek)

569
00:31:19,844 --> 00:31:23,442
- You can cover yourself with this.
- No, it's fine.

570
00:31:24,868 --> 00:31:27,829
- Your legs must be cold.
- He's still taking care of her.

571
00:31:29,606 --> 00:31:34,800
(But it's still hard to
say the first word.)

572
00:31:37,229 --> 00:31:39,149
I'm sorry for making you wait.

573
00:31:42,791 --> 00:31:44,362
I'm really sorry.

574
00:31:46,714 --> 00:31:49,763
(Won-jae is still quiet.)

575
00:31:50,722 --> 00:31:55,157
(Did his feelings change?)

576
00:31:55,877 --> 00:31:57,146
Honestly...

577
00:31:58,265 --> 00:32:04,207
I've been waiting for you to get
back and call me the whole day.

578
00:32:04,615 --> 00:32:06,377
I didn't need anything else.

579
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:12,856
(Da-Na can't say anything.)

580
00:32:13,831 --> 00:32:16,443
You should've told me
if you couldn't make it.

581
00:32:16,874 --> 00:32:18,667
Hmm... I'm sorry...

582
00:32:20,244 --> 00:32:24,991
I could've waited as long as you
wanted me to before the 24 hours was up.

583
00:32:27,585 --> 00:32:29,688
Waiting isn't a problem.

584
00:32:30,906 --> 00:32:32,604
I was just waiting...

585
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:37,068
for the call that you got back.

586
00:32:38,175 --> 00:32:39,175
I'm sorry.

587
00:32:40,948 --> 00:32:42,829
I'm sorry for making you come find me.

588
00:32:44,507 --> 00:32:47,222
Nothing happened, right?
Did you get hurt or something?

589
00:32:47,247 --> 00:32:49,343
No, it's nothing like that.

590
00:32:49,999 --> 00:32:53,983
(While waiting, his nervousness
and worry had grown.)

591
00:32:55,170 --> 00:32:58,257
You must've felt horrible while
you were waiting. I'm really sorry.

592
00:33:01,598 --> 00:33:03,494
Honestly, I did feel horrible earlier.

593
00:33:04,042 --> 00:33:06,013
But I feel better after seeing you now.

594
00:33:06,607 --> 00:33:08,435
I'm glad that I can at least see you now.

595
00:33:08,664 --> 00:33:10,794
He's really a Love Catcher, isn't he?

596
00:33:12,267 --> 00:33:13,667
Why do you look so upset?

597
00:33:14,762 --> 00:33:17,396
Smile for me. You look
really pretty when you smile.

598
00:33:17,421 --> 00:33:19,352
Oh, Won-jae!

599
00:33:20,443 --> 00:33:22,363
It's natural that she's in a predicament.

600
00:33:23,692 --> 00:33:25,200
So did you make up your mind?

601
00:33:28,966 --> 00:33:30,529
I'm not sure.

602
00:33:32,904 --> 00:33:35,678
(After waiting a long time, the
only answer he gets is uncertainty.)

603
00:33:35,703 --> 00:33:41,318
I think it really hit him for the first
time that Da-Na is in a dilemma. Right?

604
00:33:41,343 --> 00:33:42,717
Yes, that's right.

605
00:33:45,375 --> 00:33:50,104
(His heart crumbles at her answer.)

606
00:33:51,850 --> 00:33:53,783
I don't know how Da-Na feels.

607
00:33:53,808 --> 00:33:56,589
(Would it have been better not to ask her?)

608
00:33:57,545 --> 00:33:59,807
No one knows your identity except for you.

609
00:34:00,570 --> 00:34:01,570
Right?

610
00:34:02,829 --> 00:34:03,829
But if...

611
00:34:06,691 --> 00:34:08,881
if you're a Money Catcher...

612
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:10,960
If you are...

613
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:15,020
and you're really sure...

614
00:34:16,355 --> 00:34:18,779
that I'm a Love Catcher...

615
00:34:19,514 --> 00:34:21,124
Please don't do this.

616
00:34:23,374 --> 00:34:24,715
Then choose me.

617
00:34:26,131 --> 00:34:27,584
How can both of them say that?

618
00:34:27,609 --> 00:34:28,918
How can they say the same thing?

619
00:34:28,943 --> 00:34:31,636
- They don't care about her identity.
- It means nothing.

620
00:34:31,661 --> 00:34:34,789
They're not interested.
They just like Da-Na.

621
00:34:34,814 --> 00:34:35,814
This is crazy.

622
00:34:37,342 --> 00:34:41,430
Then choose me.

623
00:34:42,551 --> 00:34:44,543
(Close)

624
00:34:46,659 --> 00:34:49,757
(That's what he's been wanting
to tell her after all this time.)

625
00:34:52,826 --> 00:34:54,255
What are you saying?

626
00:34:54,702 --> 00:34:56,669
I know. It's nonsense.

627
00:34:58,307 --> 00:35:01,585
But I want you to at
least choose me for this.

628
00:35:08,532 --> 00:35:09,532
You promised, okay?

629
00:35:12,629 --> 00:35:14,267
Promise me one more time.

630
00:35:14,594 --> 00:35:18,801
(He's expressing his
desperation like a joke.)

631
00:35:19,585 --> 00:35:21,854
Gosh, Da-Na is in such a tough situation.

632
00:35:23,432 --> 00:35:27,629
(Da-Na can't easily reach out.)

633
00:35:28,634 --> 00:35:31,308
I'm sorry.

634
00:35:33,973 --> 00:35:36,403
She didn't promise him.
She didn't do a pinky promise.

635
00:35:36,428 --> 00:35:38,881
Did she decide to go with Ji-min?

636
00:35:41,637 --> 00:35:42,637
I'm sorry.

637
00:35:42,662 --> 00:35:46,125
(In the end, Da-Na didn't promise him.)

638
00:35:47,221 --> 00:35:51,662
(She apologized instead of
promising him... What did she decide?)

639
00:35:52,629 --> 00:35:56,540
(What results will they face...?)

640
00:35:57,546 --> 00:35:58,855
I'm back.

641
00:35:59,189 --> 00:36:00,989
Why are you so down though?

642
00:36:01,872 --> 00:36:04,406
- Did you have fun?
- Yeah.

643
00:36:06,453 --> 00:36:07,453
What's wrong?

644
00:36:08,653 --> 00:36:10,684
I'm having a mental breakdown.

645
00:36:10,987 --> 00:36:12,766
- Why?
- Why?

646
00:36:13,084 --> 00:36:14,830
I don't know where I should start.

647
00:36:15,167 --> 00:36:16,767
Did she change her mind?

648
00:36:17,074 --> 00:36:20,145
(Women's powder room)

649
00:36:21,404 --> 00:36:24,803
Everyone is in complicated
situations for different reasons.

650
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:30,259
(Last time to get ready before
the final selection/Glance)

651
00:36:31,049 --> 00:36:32,049
Da-Na.

652
00:36:35,715 --> 00:36:37,425
Toss me over there.

653
00:36:38,534 --> 00:36:41,811
What's wrong with you? You did fine.

654
00:36:42,004 --> 00:36:44,973
No. Why is it so hard?

655
00:36:46,667 --> 00:36:48,343
- What's hard?
- Exactly...

656
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,639
I can't choose...

657
00:36:53,139 --> 00:36:56,339
(Da-na's feelings are
as complicated as ever...)

658
00:36:56,364 --> 00:36:59,479
(Remaining time until the final selection)

659
00:36:59,504 --> 00:37:01,355
God, I wonder what will happen.

660
00:37:03,488 --> 00:37:05,555
I think she's gonna choose you.

661
00:37:06,346 --> 00:37:08,080
That's what my hunch says.

662
00:37:08,508 --> 00:37:11,699
- Even now?
- Yeah. I think she's gonna pick you.

663
00:37:13,115 --> 00:37:14,315
That's how I feel.

664
00:37:16,041 --> 00:37:17,041
What's wrong?

665
00:37:17,965 --> 00:37:19,567
I really, really enjoyed the date.

666
00:37:19,592 --> 00:37:22,972
It was really fun, and Jae-hyung
was funny and considerate.

667
00:37:24,200 --> 00:37:28,343
But I feel really apologetic.

668
00:37:29,238 --> 00:37:31,642
I don't know if I made
the right choice or not.

669
00:37:32,444 --> 00:37:34,304
Isn't that what everybody thinks?

670
00:37:35,605 --> 00:37:39,451
(It's hard to be certain
of anything right now.)

671
00:37:39,708 --> 00:37:44,765
(Remaining time until the final selection)

672
00:37:44,790 --> 00:37:47,664
(Men's dorm)

673
00:37:48,393 --> 00:37:49,908
Did you make up your mind?

674
00:37:50,457 --> 00:37:54,148
I have to decide now.
There's not much time left.

675
00:37:56,633 --> 00:37:58,695
(Ji-min drops his gaze.)

676
00:37:58,720 --> 00:38:02,366
I'm probably gonna go with the person

677
00:38:03,397 --> 00:38:05,289
I've liked ever since the beginning.

678
00:38:06,308 --> 00:38:10,104
The moment I was sure, I didn't
look at anyone else and decided that...

679
00:38:11,016 --> 00:38:12,796
I was going to choose her.

680
00:38:12,821 --> 00:38:14,235
It's a declaration of war.

681
00:38:15,692 --> 00:38:17,613
Same here. The moment I was sure...

682
00:38:19,493 --> 00:38:20,941
she was the only one for me.

683
00:38:23,086 --> 00:38:26,864
(Whose heart will reach hers?)

684
00:38:31,307 --> 00:38:34,064
It's so scary now.

685
00:38:34,569 --> 00:38:37,402
I think I know your identity now.

686
00:38:38,259 --> 00:38:39,778
There's a reason you must be nervous.

687
00:38:39,803 --> 00:38:41,510
- What?
- Because she's a Love Catcher?

688
00:38:41,853 --> 00:38:43,559
Because she's a Money Catcher?

689
00:38:43,584 --> 00:38:45,708
Do you think that the
person you're going to

690
00:38:45,733 --> 00:38:47,772
choose is a Love Catcher
or a Money Catcher?

691
00:38:47,797 --> 00:38:48,797
I don't know.

692
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:52,037
- I think he's a Money Catcher.
- So do I...

693
00:38:52,062 --> 00:38:54,666
If they're all Money Catchers,
then who are the Love Catchers?

694
00:38:54,691 --> 00:38:57,542
- You think he's a Money Catcher, too?
- I have no idea.

695
00:38:57,830 --> 00:38:58,981
I seriously don't know.

696
00:38:59,006 --> 00:39:01,602
I really don't know. The
guys are ambiguous.

697
00:39:01,627 --> 00:39:03,835
I have no clue, but I just
said he's a Money Catcher.

698
00:39:04,258 --> 00:39:07,831
- It's ambiguous.
- I think Su-won is a Love Catcher though.

699
00:39:08,731 --> 00:39:10,040
(Confused)

700
00:39:10,330 --> 00:39:15,879
If I were you, I bet Su-won
has a lot on his mind.

701
00:39:16,359 --> 00:39:18,066
- Because he's worried?
- Yeah.

702
00:39:18,431 --> 00:39:21,846
Wow, if Ha-neul is really a
Money Catcher... then, wow...

703
00:39:22,413 --> 00:39:24,127
I'm super nervous. Am I the only one?

704
00:39:24,152 --> 00:39:25,692
No, of course we're nervous.

705
00:39:28,483 --> 00:39:30,491
What about you? I'm curious about you.

706
00:39:31,404 --> 00:39:32,404
I'm anxious.

707
00:39:35,106 --> 00:39:36,815
God, I feel so weird.

708
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:44,082
(Remaining time until the final selection)

709
00:39:44,107 --> 00:39:48,016
(Today's Question: Who
are the Love Catchers?)

710
00:39:48,048 --> 00:39:50,845
Now it's time for the final selection.

711
00:39:50,870 --> 00:39:53,333
Did everyone decide?
We have to decide, too.

712
00:39:53,732 --> 00:39:54,859
What do you think?

713
00:39:54,884 --> 00:39:57,519
- Who did I choose again?
- This is tough.

714
00:39:57,686 --> 00:40:01,744
Was Da-Na sorry because
she's a Love Catcher?

715
00:40:02,112 --> 00:40:04,113
(Sunny is quietly putting up her cards.)

716
00:40:04,138 --> 00:40:08,473
Won-jae, Su-won, Yeo-min, and Ji-min.

717
00:40:08,979 --> 00:40:13,034
I just picked the people I'm drawn to.

718
00:40:13,059 --> 00:40:16,349
Aren't you drawn to someone
because they're sincere?

719
00:40:16,374 --> 00:40:18,702
So I picked the ones
we are a bit more curious

720
00:40:18,727 --> 00:40:21,153
about and want to know
what happens to them next.

721
00:40:22,118 --> 00:40:24,158
That's who I chose.

722
00:40:24,558 --> 00:40:29,115
I pick these three: Won-jae,
Yeo-min, and Su-won.

723
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:31,438
I just took out everyone who
seemed like Money Catchers,

724
00:40:31,463 --> 00:40:33,128
and they were the ones left.

725
00:40:33,153 --> 00:40:35,051
- It's pretty much the same for me.
- Really?

726
00:40:35,076 --> 00:40:39,715
I pick Won-jae, Su-won, and Yeo-min.

727
00:40:40,027 --> 00:40:42,661
- I'm thinking about Da-Na.
- Da-Na?

728
00:40:43,063 --> 00:40:45,499
- I was stuck, so I looked at my outfit.
- Again?

729
00:40:46,669 --> 00:40:47,891
I have three buckles.

730
00:40:48,346 --> 00:40:49,346
I see.

731
00:40:49,473 --> 00:40:52,855
- So there are three Love Catchers.
- Alright.

732
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:55,254
I pick Won-jae and Su-won.

733
00:40:55,691 --> 00:40:57,624
Everyone's picking those two.

734
00:40:58,133 --> 00:41:02,688
Ha-neul, Ji-min, and Dana.

735
00:41:04,029 --> 00:41:08,084
I'm sure that Won-jae is a Love Catcher.

736
00:41:08,109 --> 00:41:12,836
I think these participants
are definitely Love Catchers.

737
00:41:13,508 --> 00:41:16,127
That's who I'm sure of so far.

738
00:41:16,598 --> 00:41:21,280
I kept thinking that
Ji-min is a Money Catcher.

739
00:41:22,016 --> 00:41:23,587
If you're a Money Catcher...

740
00:41:24,825 --> 00:41:26,724
choose me to be safe, okay?

741
00:41:27,435 --> 00:41:28,736
- Wow, I was... - He meant it?

742
00:41:28,761 --> 00:41:32,031
- As an actor, you didn't think
he was faking it? - No, his emotions...

743
00:41:32,056 --> 00:41:34,200
So I bet my all on him.

744
00:41:34,225 --> 00:41:37,347
I think Ha-neul and Ji-min are...

745
00:41:37,663 --> 00:41:38,864
a union of Money Catchers.

746
00:41:38,889 --> 00:41:43,114
Seriously? Ji-min, too? I think
he's a real Love Catcher though.

747
00:41:43,139 --> 00:41:48,062
Those who get it right
will get one coin, not two.

748
00:41:48,838 --> 00:41:52,116
But you will get one coin per right answer.

749
00:41:52,141 --> 00:41:55,494
- You could turn the tables.
- I'm sure I got at least one right.

750
00:41:55,519 --> 00:41:59,091
Now, let's check the results
we were all curious about.

751
00:41:59,364 --> 00:42:00,792
(It will be revealed right now!)

752
00:42:00,817 --> 00:42:03,049
I just hope nothing scary will happen.

753
00:42:03,074 --> 00:42:04,074
Please.

754
00:42:09,916 --> 00:42:10,916
Matching rings?

755
00:42:10,941 --> 00:42:13,607
- The Love Catcher couples will get rings.
- That's right.

756
00:42:13,750 --> 00:42:16,023
I want to see them put those rings on.

757
00:42:19,261 --> 00:42:21,745
(1. Each of the
participants will take the box

758
00:42:21,770 --> 00:42:24,738
containing their identity
and stand in their position.)

759
00:42:24,763 --> 00:42:26,637
I bet they're really nervous.

760
00:42:27,690 --> 00:42:34,102
(2. They will go to their final
choice and deliver their identity box.)

761
00:42:37,016 --> 00:42:40,751
(3. If they choose each
other, they will open

762
00:42:40,776 --> 00:42:44,511
each other's boxes to
check their identities.)

763
00:42:48,153 --> 00:42:52,179
(4. If they don't get selected,
they will deliver their

764
00:42:52,204 --> 00:42:55,848
identity box to the person
they want and leave.)

765
00:42:59,706 --> 00:43:01,873
- Who's going first?
- Who is it?

766
00:43:02,367 --> 00:43:04,423
- Su-won?
- It's Su-won.

767
00:43:04,774 --> 00:43:06,822
Gosh, he must be really nervous.

768
00:43:06,847 --> 00:43:09,253
(Will Ha-neul choose Ha-neul as always?)

769
00:43:09,278 --> 00:43:12,145
- He'll go to Ha-neul.
- I'm sure he will.

770
00:43:18,178 --> 00:43:20,824
- Oh, why is he...?
- Why is he so slow?

771
00:43:20,849 --> 00:43:22,776
He must be nervous.

772
00:43:26,757 --> 00:43:27,824
Why did he stop?

773
00:43:28,911 --> 00:43:29,978
What's going on?

774
00:43:30,003 --> 00:43:33,262
This is very different from
the Su-won we've seen so far.

775
00:43:33,685 --> 00:43:34,939
What's happening?

776
00:43:35,114 --> 00:43:36,114
What is it?

777
00:43:36,569 --> 00:43:40,023
I guess they get nervous at that moment
even if they know their choice.

778
00:43:40,888 --> 00:43:44,368
(Ha-neul can't look at him.)

779
00:43:44,790 --> 00:43:48,452
(Su-won is hesitating. Is he a
Money Catcher or a Love Catcher?)

780
00:43:49,766 --> 00:43:52,616
(Jung Su-won has selected Lee Ha-neul.)

781
00:43:52,641 --> 00:43:54,460
He really has eyes for only one person!

782
00:43:54,485 --> 00:43:55,654
Ha-neul...

783
00:43:57,435 --> 00:44:00,277
Thanks for making my heart
flutter while we were here.

784
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:03,280
I hope tomorrow's sky
will be beautiful, too.

785
00:44:03,511 --> 00:44:05,258
(Giving the girls a heart attack)

786
00:44:05,283 --> 00:44:06,838
(What's with that line?)

787
00:44:06,863 --> 00:44:08,744
I kind of got goosebumps.

788
00:44:09,177 --> 00:44:11,462
I hope tomorrow's sky
will be beautiful, too.

789
00:44:13,165 --> 00:44:14,899
Why does my heart flutter?

790
00:44:15,499 --> 00:44:18,810
(Su-won gives her the
box with his identity inside.)

791
00:44:18,835 --> 00:44:21,424
- Su-won is a Love Catcher, right?
- Please.

792
00:44:22,209 --> 00:44:24,500
(Does she feel the same way?)

793
00:44:25,114 --> 00:44:28,503
Ha-neul has to choose Su-won
in order to know his identity.

794
00:44:28,713 --> 00:44:30,780
If they're not Love Catchers...

795
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:35,670
It's Jae-hyung.

796
00:44:38,142 --> 00:44:41,956
(This moment, he thinks about
all the memories at Love Mansion.)

797
00:44:42,944 --> 00:44:45,586
I'm really curious about Jae-hyung.

798
00:44:45,935 --> 00:44:46,935
Seriously.

799
00:44:46,960 --> 00:44:48,757
(Who will be his final selection?)

800
00:44:50,069 --> 00:44:53,252
(In-seong, the one he enjoyed
the final date with at the beach?)

801
00:44:53,681 --> 00:44:56,931
(Or Da-Na, the one who made
him feel true nervousness?)

802
00:44:57,891 --> 00:45:01,895
(Or is there someone
else on his mind?)

803
00:45:03,294 --> 00:45:05,567
(Jae-hyung suddenly turns his direction.)

804
00:45:05,592 --> 00:45:07,593
- Where is he going?
- What's happening?

805
00:45:08,334 --> 00:45:11,143
(Seo Jae-hyung has selected...)

806
00:45:11,168 --> 00:45:15,459
(Lee In-seong.)

807
00:45:17,032 --> 00:45:18,334
I had fun today.

808
00:45:21,633 --> 00:45:23,053
I want to have more fun with you.

809
00:45:23,078 --> 00:45:26,525
- Oh my goodness!
- Thank you.

810
00:45:27,958 --> 00:45:29,322
In-seong...

811
00:45:29,832 --> 00:45:32,136
Why does her expression look so cold?

812
00:45:32,432 --> 00:45:34,114
Gosh, I'm nervous.

813
00:45:34,139 --> 00:45:35,965
(In-seong's expression is unreadable.)

814
00:45:36,492 --> 00:45:40,214
(She can only check his
identity if she picks him.)

815
00:45:42,608 --> 00:45:43,933
Won-jae, let's go

816
00:45:45,791 --> 00:45:48,460
(He quickly passes by Ji-min.)

817
00:45:49,077 --> 00:45:51,393
(Ji-min watches Won-jae's back.)

818
00:45:52,841 --> 00:45:54,041
It's Da-Na, right?

819
00:45:54,714 --> 00:45:55,714
Probably.

820
00:45:56,320 --> 00:45:59,124
If only she had linked
her pinky with his...

821
00:45:59,149 --> 00:46:00,848
If she had, he would've run to her.

822
00:46:01,883 --> 00:46:03,161
Yes, that's like him.

823
00:46:03,186 --> 00:46:04,486
He's not sure, but...

824
00:46:04,511 --> 00:46:08,013
(He didn't get a clear answer
from the wavering Da-Na.)

825
00:46:08,789 --> 00:46:12,334
(Does he still feel the
same way about her?)

826
00:46:13,506 --> 00:46:14,906
Is he going to Da-Na?

827
00:46:16,510 --> 00:46:18,049
- Yeo-min.
- I'm nervous!

828
00:46:18,074 --> 00:46:20,139
I wish things worked out for her.

829
00:46:21,394 --> 00:46:26,603
(Yeo-min isn't his choice.)

830
00:46:28,242 --> 00:46:30,509
It's such a hard time for Yeo-min.

831
00:46:33,996 --> 00:46:35,901
He's firmly heading towards her.

832
00:46:39,647 --> 00:46:44,146
(Kang Won-jae has selected Jung Da-Na.)

833
00:46:44,923 --> 00:46:49,207
(Ji-min is also watching his selection.)

834
00:46:50,021 --> 00:46:51,553
Don't think about anything else.

835
00:46:52,934 --> 00:46:55,064
Just know that this is my sincerity.

836
00:46:56,130 --> 00:46:59,233
(You really are a Love Catcher!)

837
00:46:59,258 --> 00:47:00,791
His words are sad, too.

838
00:47:01,486 --> 00:47:03,661
Just know that this is my sincerity.

839
00:47:08,015 --> 00:47:11,111
- He's the one we firmly believe
is a Love Catcher. - Won-jae...

840
00:47:11,136 --> 00:47:13,191
(Is he a Love Catcher
who has come to find love?)

841
00:47:13,216 --> 00:47:15,060
(Or is he a Money
Catcher putting on an act?)

842
00:47:16,215 --> 00:47:20,248
(Did Won-jae's sincerity reach her?)

843
00:47:21,184 --> 00:47:23,800
(On his way back, they
see each other again.)

844
00:47:24,477 --> 00:47:27,858
(They avoid eye contact.)

845
00:47:28,625 --> 00:47:32,722
(Are they choosing the same person?)

846
00:47:35,206 --> 00:47:37,878
(He can't hide his nervousness.)

847
00:47:37,903 --> 00:47:39,945
Won-jae is nervous.

848
00:47:41,237 --> 00:47:42,606
Ji-min.

849
00:47:46,693 --> 00:47:49,256
His expression is different from usual.

850
00:47:51,535 --> 00:47:54,214
(Will he choose Ha-neul, the one
who he was always close with?)

851
00:47:54,239 --> 00:47:57,185
(Or Da-Na, the one he cried
while making a confession to?)

852
00:47:57,210 --> 00:48:00,203
(Who will Ji-min select?)

853
00:48:01,501 --> 00:48:03,461
Su-won can't take his eyes off of Ji-min.

854
00:48:03,749 --> 00:48:06,170
They both can't for different reasons.

855
00:48:06,653 --> 00:48:10,498
(Ji-min stops in his tracks.)

856
00:48:10,523 --> 00:48:13,552
What's going on? Why is he doing
that like he's a Money Catcher?

857
00:48:13,577 --> 00:48:15,474
Don't do that! What are you doing?

858
00:48:15,922 --> 00:48:16,922
He's pondering?

859
00:48:17,209 --> 00:48:19,010
Don't do it, Ji-min.

860
00:48:19,554 --> 00:48:23,101
(Who is the one that is
making him think so hard?)

861
00:48:25,449 --> 00:48:28,566
(Ji-min continues walking.)

862
00:48:29,040 --> 00:48:30,879
(Is he going to Ha-neul?)

863
00:48:31,133 --> 00:48:33,160
- Really?
- For real?

864
00:48:35,253 --> 00:48:36,766
(He passes by her.)

865
00:48:36,791 --> 00:48:38,023
Oh, he passed by.

866
00:48:38,586 --> 00:48:40,636
- He'll probably go to Da-Na.
- Yeah.

867
00:48:42,196 --> 00:48:45,696
(The closer Ji-min goes to Da-Na,
the stiffer Won-jae's expression gets.)

868
00:48:45,721 --> 00:48:49,309
Oh gosh, I feel bad for
Won-jae. This is driving me crazy.

869
00:48:50,042 --> 00:48:53,911
(Da-Na was already chosen by Won-jae.)

870
00:48:54,606 --> 00:49:01,561
(Ahn Ji-min has selected Jung Da-Na.)

871
00:49:02,701 --> 00:49:04,301
If it's okay with you...

872
00:49:07,833 --> 00:49:09,937
I want to see you again.

873
00:49:12,878 --> 00:49:15,586
- Is Dana a Love Catcher?
- Is she a Money Catcher?

874
00:49:19,328 --> 00:49:20,328
Thanks.

875
00:49:21,060 --> 00:49:22,935
- I had fun.
- Thanks.

876
00:49:24,765 --> 00:49:28,664
Da-Na has been selected
by Won-jae and Ji-min.

877
00:49:28,689 --> 00:49:31,422
I can't wait to find out who she chooses.

878
00:49:32,946 --> 00:49:38,296
(How will their love triangle end?)

879
00:49:38,321 --> 00:49:39,850
Gosh, this is suffocating.

880
00:49:42,036 --> 00:49:44,340
- The men are done choosing.
- Right.

881
00:49:44,642 --> 00:49:45,785
- They're all done?
- Yes.

882
00:49:45,810 --> 00:49:49,414
Everyone's identities will be revealed
after the women make their choices.

883
00:49:49,838 --> 00:49:52,243
Here it comes. Something
big is going to happen.

884
00:49:54,135 --> 00:49:57,646
- What do we do?
- Oh, Yeo-min!

885
00:49:57,678 --> 00:50:00,159
(Yeo-min, the first one,
starts making her way.)

886
00:50:02,659 --> 00:50:07,162
(She hadn't gotten selected by anyone.)

887
00:50:08,642 --> 00:50:10,294
Yeo-min, give it to me.

888
00:50:11,290 --> 00:50:13,981
- Won't she go to Won-jae?
- I think so.

889
00:50:14,006 --> 00:50:17,120
Is it Won-jae, the one she
lost because of wrong timing?)

890
00:50:19,554 --> 00:50:23,529
(Yeo-min slowly walks towards him.)

891
00:50:23,993 --> 00:50:25,260
Why are you crying?

892
00:50:25,285 --> 00:50:28,296
(Lee Yeo-min has selected Kang Won-jae.)

893
00:50:28,321 --> 00:50:31,261
Thank you so much for coming
to pick me up on the first day.

894
00:50:32,600 --> 00:50:36,877
I meant all the things I did
for you and the things I said.

895
00:50:38,152 --> 00:50:39,819
Thank you for everything.

896
00:50:41,155 --> 00:50:42,487
I want to thank you, too.

897
00:50:43,045 --> 00:50:45,362
- Yeo-min is a Love Catcher!
- She's a Love Catcher.

898
00:50:45,387 --> 00:50:48,134
She said she really
meant it and thanked him.

899
00:50:52,450 --> 00:50:55,365
- Yeo-min is seriously so cool.
- She's awesome.

900
00:50:55,390 --> 00:50:57,313
(She calmly says her goodbye and leaves.)

901
00:50:58,233 --> 00:51:01,348
(Her last words that she was sincere)

902
00:51:02,359 --> 00:51:05,661
- Is her identity being revealed now?
- Yes.

903
00:51:09,024 --> 00:51:10,429
(I chose Yeo-min, too.)

904
00:51:10,454 --> 00:51:11,454
Thank God.

905
00:51:11,662 --> 00:51:14,226
(I'm the only one who
didn't choose... Yeo-min.)

906
00:51:15,151 --> 00:51:17,588
- She's a Love Catcher, right?
- She is.

907
00:51:19,001 --> 00:51:22,605
(He has to check her identity alone.)

908
00:51:23,223 --> 00:51:24,223
Money.

909
00:51:26,932 --> 00:51:30,252
(Won-jae stares at her
identity for a long time.)

910
00:51:30,277 --> 00:51:31,873
What's with that reaction?

911
00:51:31,898 --> 00:51:34,165
I'd rather she be a Money Catcher.

912
00:51:36,832 --> 00:51:39,055
(Love? Money?)

913
00:51:39,080 --> 00:51:41,478
(Lee Yeo-min = Money Catcher)

914
00:51:44,253 --> 00:51:46,786
- Damn it.
- "Damn it"?

915
00:51:46,811 --> 00:51:48,383
- For real?
- What's this?

916
00:51:48,662 --> 00:51:51,030
Oh my god. I'm speechless.

917
00:51:51,070 --> 00:51:53,096
My neck...

918
00:51:53,121 --> 00:51:56,302
That's why she said everything
she did to him was sincere!

919
00:51:56,327 --> 00:51:57,741
Because she's a Money Catcher!

920
00:51:57,766 --> 00:52:01,506
- Or maybe because she really liked him.
- Precisely.

921
00:52:01,789 --> 00:52:03,066
Oh my goodness.

922
00:52:03,548 --> 00:52:06,972
(After checking her identity,
he's overwhelmed with bitterness.)

923
00:52:07,428 --> 00:52:10,477
- Wow, but she really seemed like
a Love Catcher. - She did.

924
00:52:10,795 --> 00:52:13,575
- I'm not off to a bad start.
- I think I'm doomed.

925
00:52:17,836 --> 00:52:18,836
In-seong.

926
00:52:19,320 --> 00:52:21,323
She seemed to have a lot on her mind.

927
00:52:22,202 --> 00:52:25,621
(Will she choose Ji-min, the one she
had a good time doing the challenge with?)

928
00:52:27,905 --> 00:52:33,087
(Or Jae-hyung, the one who
chose her after their last date?)

929
00:52:34,047 --> 00:52:37,051
(They don't know each other's
identities, so she's more careful.)

930
00:52:37,076 --> 00:52:38,577
Won't she go to Jae-hyung?

931
00:52:38,602 --> 00:52:40,469
(Jae-hyung is to her right.)

932
00:52:42,250 --> 00:52:44,187
(Ji-min is to her left.)

933
00:52:45,134 --> 00:52:51,781
(In-seong, who had hesitated,
heads towards Jae-hyung.)

934
00:52:52,088 --> 00:52:54,453
- For real?
- He can't hide his joy.

935
00:52:54,478 --> 00:52:57,678
It's been a while since I've seen
the right corner of his lips go up?

936
00:52:58,093 --> 00:53:00,626
He suddenly seems like a Love Catcher.

937
00:53:00,651 --> 00:53:04,017
(Lee In-seong has selected Seo Jae-hyung.)

938
00:53:04,919 --> 00:53:08,696
I truly had a great time today.

939
00:53:09,525 --> 00:53:10,525
Me, too.

940
00:53:10,732 --> 00:53:12,709
She said "truly." She's a Money Catcher.

941
00:53:12,734 --> 00:53:13,734
"Truly."

942
00:53:13,759 --> 00:53:17,038
- Don't say that word.
- "I truly had a great time today."

943
00:53:17,393 --> 00:53:20,083
- If she said that, that means...
- She's a Money Catcher?

944
00:53:21,710 --> 00:53:25,382
(It's time to check
each other's identities.)

945
00:53:27,188 --> 00:53:28,388
Should we open it?

946
00:53:29,563 --> 00:53:30,563
Yeah.

947
00:53:33,703 --> 00:53:35,970
I hope they're both Love Catchers!

948
00:53:35,995 --> 00:53:38,292
(What are their identities?)

949
00:53:38,967 --> 00:53:40,100
At the same time?

950
00:53:42,752 --> 00:53:44,926
- Look at their expressions.
- What? Why?

951
00:53:44,951 --> 00:53:46,301
They're relieved!

952
00:53:47,320 --> 00:53:48,320
I'm glad.

953
00:53:49,414 --> 00:53:51,214
- I'm glad.
- I'm so glad.

954
00:53:51,697 --> 00:53:53,133
Are they both Money Catchers?

955
00:53:53,158 --> 00:53:54,189
Gosh, what a relief.

956
00:53:54,214 --> 00:53:56,589
- They're either both Love
or both Money, right? - Yup.

957
00:53:56,997 --> 00:53:58,997
- I'm glad.
- This is better.

958
00:54:00,649 --> 00:54:02,390
This is actually better.

959
00:54:02,415 --> 00:54:03,482
What's going on?

960
00:54:03,507 --> 00:54:05,465
- Should we check one more time?
- Yeah.

961
00:54:05,490 --> 00:54:07,736
They're Money Catchers.
They tend to check twice.

962
00:54:09,170 --> 00:54:11,519
"Did I see it wrong?"
They tend to check twice.

963
00:54:11,544 --> 00:54:13,479
- Should we check one more time?
- Yeah.

964
00:54:14,571 --> 00:54:16,071
In-seong is...

965
00:54:18,819 --> 00:54:22,833
- She's a Money Catcher! Money, money!
- Yeah, it worked out better.

966
00:54:22,858 --> 00:54:24,258
What about Jae-hyung?

967
00:54:25,631 --> 00:54:27,543
- He's a Money Catcher.
- He's Money.

968
00:54:31,740 --> 00:54:34,033
- They're a Money Catcher couple.
- Money, money.

969
00:54:34,060 --> 00:54:35,536
I got it all right!

970
00:54:37,031 --> 00:54:38,380
Oh my god. That's crazy.

971
00:54:38,405 --> 00:54:42,160
- If the rest are Love Catchers...
- Won't you win first place?

972
00:54:42,185 --> 00:54:44,052
There should be no more Money Catchers.

973
00:54:45,061 --> 00:54:49,398
(The birth of a Money Catcher couple)

974
00:54:50,250 --> 00:54:52,419
(They crack up at each other's identities.)

975
00:54:52,451 --> 00:54:54,546
Gosh, this is better.

976
00:54:55,876 --> 00:54:57,837
Jinx.

977
00:54:59,683 --> 00:55:00,816
They're a couple.

978
00:55:00,841 --> 00:55:03,216
- They're the most interesting couple.
- This is funny.

979
00:55:03,241 --> 00:55:05,488
- It's interesting.
- It's interesting.

980
00:55:05,809 --> 00:55:06,943
"It's interesting."

981
00:55:07,445 --> 00:55:10,409
Now I know why Jae-hyung
looked so uncomfortable!

982
00:55:10,434 --> 00:55:12,832
- That's because he's a Money Catcher!
- He had to hide it.

983
00:55:12,857 --> 00:55:15,146
- He had to keep lying.
- He looks relaxed now.

984
00:55:15,171 --> 00:55:16,171
I see now.

985
00:55:19,850 --> 00:55:21,250
Good work, Jae-hyung.

986
00:55:21,551 --> 00:55:23,328
I feel at ease now.

987
00:55:23,951 --> 00:55:28,180
(The third one to go is Ha-neul.)

988
00:55:28,553 --> 00:55:30,923
(Everyone is curious
about Ha-neul's choice.)

989
00:55:30,948 --> 00:55:33,306
- What do we do?
- This is really important.

990
00:55:35,480 --> 00:55:38,170
(Ha-neul walks without
a smile on her face.)

991
00:55:38,195 --> 00:55:41,044
She's wearing the most
makeup today out of all the days.

992
00:55:41,069 --> 00:55:43,246
Oh, did she perhaps
paint a mole on her face?

993
00:55:45,361 --> 00:55:48,106
(Who will she choose?)

994
00:55:49,063 --> 00:55:53,555
(Is it Su-won, like everyone wishes?)

995
00:55:55,467 --> 00:55:59,103
(Will her footsteps reach him?)

996
00:55:59,128 --> 00:56:01,220
(Or will she go to Ji-min,
who has always been by

997
00:56:01,245 --> 00:56:03,377
her side whenever she was
going through hardships?)

998
00:56:03,402 --> 00:56:06,452
(If she doesn't choose Su-won,
they will fail to become a couple.)

999
00:56:07,493 --> 00:56:11,200
(What is her final selection?)

1000
00:56:15,067 --> 00:56:16,988
I thought I was going
to get a heart attack!

1001
00:56:17,013 --> 00:56:19,943
(Lee Ha-neul has chosen Jung Su-won.)

1002
00:56:19,967 --> 00:56:22,390
They both have to be Love Catchers.

1003
00:56:22,415 --> 00:56:24,352
They're our official couple.

1004
00:56:24,377 --> 00:56:26,479
(Nervous)

1005
00:56:27,899 --> 00:56:29,970
- You knew I would come, right?
- Huh?

1006
00:56:29,995 --> 00:56:31,734
You knew I would come, right?

1007
00:56:31,940 --> 00:56:33,649
I was... I was hoping you would.

1008
00:56:35,770 --> 00:56:37,104
Do I give it to you?

1009
00:56:38,035 --> 00:56:39,400
Thanks for coming.

1010
00:56:41,134 --> 00:56:43,803
She's not looking at him.

1011
00:56:44,121 --> 00:56:47,471
- I feel uneasy!
- No, it can't be!

1012
00:56:48,626 --> 00:56:49,626
No, no.

1013
00:56:50,030 --> 00:56:51,452
Thanks for coming.

1014
00:56:52,970 --> 00:56:54,170
Oh, what was that?

1015
00:56:55,833 --> 00:56:58,491
Their identities are important.

1016
00:56:58,788 --> 00:56:59,788
Yeah.

1017
00:57:00,335 --> 00:57:02,226
Please both be Love Catchers.

1018
00:57:03,388 --> 00:57:04,983
- Aren't you nervous?
- Huh?

1019
00:57:06,789 --> 00:57:07,789
I am.

1020
00:57:08,321 --> 00:57:09,854
Wow, this is really...!

1021
00:57:09,879 --> 00:57:14,309
(Are they nervous because they
don't know each other's identities?)

1022
00:57:14,334 --> 00:57:15,334
Please!

1023
00:57:15,798 --> 00:57:19,221
Why can't you look at me?

1024
00:57:20,216 --> 00:57:22,517
See? She can't make eye contact with him!

1025
00:57:24,385 --> 00:57:27,895
(Is it because she's nervous?
Or is it because she's sorry?)

1026
00:57:27,920 --> 00:57:30,517
Maybe it's because she's shy
since they're both Love Catchers!

1027
00:57:33,147 --> 00:57:36,380
Some people suspected
her of being a Money Catcher.

1028
00:57:36,405 --> 00:57:37,939
Ha-neul? No way.

1029
00:57:37,964 --> 00:57:40,028
- Is Su-won a Money Catcher?
- No, he's Love, right?

1030
00:57:40,053 --> 00:57:42,008
Should we reveal them at the same time?

1031
00:57:42,533 --> 00:57:43,533
(Nod)

1032
00:57:43,691 --> 00:57:44,691
Okay.

1033
00:57:45,045 --> 00:57:47,012
(Will they be able to smile together?)

1034
00:57:47,037 --> 00:57:50,228
(Please be Love Catchers!)

1035
00:57:50,398 --> 00:57:52,477
1, 2, 3.

1036
00:57:54,481 --> 00:57:56,570
(They opened the boxes!)

1037
00:57:57,649 --> 00:58:01,376
(Su-won and Ha-neul are checking
each other's identities at the same time.)

1038
00:58:04,112 --> 00:58:05,445
Didn't he just sigh?

1039
00:58:06,209 --> 00:58:07,399
Is that a good thing?

1040
00:58:07,424 --> 00:58:09,988
(They're not saying a word.)

1041
00:58:10,013 --> 00:58:12,284
Ha-neul shut her box, and
Su-won keeps staring at his.

1042
00:58:15,609 --> 00:58:17,934
- What's going on?
- Is she crying or laughing?

1043
00:58:17,959 --> 00:58:19,887
What's going on? What is it?

1044
00:58:20,160 --> 00:58:22,287
- Don't tell me.
- They're both Love Catchers!

1045
00:58:24,386 --> 00:58:26,688
They're Love Catchers,
right? Please say they are!

1046
00:58:27,488 --> 00:58:32,971
(Ha-neul = Money Catcher)

1047
00:58:35,676 --> 00:58:39,240
- I knew it!
- This is crazy!

1048
00:58:39,265 --> 00:58:40,846
- Money!
- Wow!

1049
00:58:41,508 --> 00:58:42,641
I got goosebumps.

1050
00:58:43,391 --> 00:58:45,314
But we thought he was a Money Catcher.

1051
00:58:45,339 --> 00:58:47,861
I think he's a Love Catcher.

1052
00:58:47,886 --> 00:58:54,304
(Su-won = Love Catcher)

1053
00:58:56,553 --> 00:58:58,555
(They were so shocked
by Ha-neul's identity

1054
00:58:58,580 --> 00:59:00,582
that they got shocked
by the coin's shadow.)

1055
00:59:01,038 --> 00:59:03,760
Oh, Su-won!

1056
00:59:03,785 --> 00:59:06,033
Oh my god, I think he'll be so heartbroken.

1057
00:59:06,057 --> 00:59:07,208
- Seriously.
- I knew it!

1058
00:59:07,233 --> 00:59:08,483
Poor Su-won.

1059
00:59:09,105 --> 00:59:12,543
Su-won was even thinking about how
they'll have a long-distance relationship.

1060
00:59:13,340 --> 00:59:15,540
Then was she playing hard-to-get?

1061
00:59:17,964 --> 00:59:18,964
Oh no.

1062
00:59:21,236 --> 00:59:23,570
Did you change your identity or...

1063
00:59:24,660 --> 00:59:26,390
were you a Money
Catcher from the beginning?

1064
00:59:27,273 --> 00:59:28,639
From the beginning.

1065
00:59:29,342 --> 00:59:32,770
(She was a Money
Catcher from the beginning.)

1066
00:59:32,795 --> 00:59:34,471
Wow, I got goosebumps!

1067
00:59:34,496 --> 00:59:36,933
It was so scary when
she said that and smiled!

1068
00:59:38,515 --> 00:59:39,782
From the beginning.

1069
00:59:39,807 --> 00:59:41,566
(Grin)

1070
00:59:42,045 --> 00:59:44,560
(We were totally fooled!)

1071
00:59:44,585 --> 00:59:48,531
Even though she had a
chance to change, she didn't.

1072
00:59:48,624 --> 00:59:52,433
She kept playing as a Money Catcher.

1073
00:59:52,746 --> 00:59:53,746
This is crazy.

1074
00:59:53,771 --> 00:59:58,740
(After checking her identity,
he can't bring himself to talk.)

1075
00:59:59,110 --> 01:00:00,578
I don't know what to say.

1076
01:00:00,603 --> 01:00:02,118
He can't believe it.

1077
01:00:02,732 --> 01:00:04,813
- Oh, man.
- This is nuts.

1078
01:00:06,943 --> 01:00:07,943
I'm sorry.

1079
01:00:10,694 --> 01:00:11,908
I really...

1080
01:00:13,487 --> 01:00:15,021
thought you were a Love Catcher.

1081
01:00:15,046 --> 01:00:17,103
Oh, Su-won. I feel so bad for him.

1082
01:00:17,128 --> 01:00:18,613
This is so shocking.

1083
01:00:18,638 --> 01:00:22,464
(He's even more shocked
because he trusted her.)

1084
01:00:29,220 --> 01:00:33,356
(Eventually, he starts to tear up...)

1085
01:00:42,006 --> 01:00:44,472
- My heart breaks.
- This is so sad.

1086
01:00:44,746 --> 01:00:47,039
I really don't know who's who anymore.

1087
01:00:49,727 --> 01:00:50,727
I'm sorry...

1088
01:00:53,606 --> 01:00:58,311
(Ha-neul, who was a Money
Catcher, walks away...)

1089
01:01:02,809 --> 01:01:04,436
Su-won, don't cry.

1090
01:01:06,173 --> 01:01:14,088
Su-won had felt really guilty
about going to Da-Na that one time.

1091
01:01:14,213 --> 01:01:16,515
Wow, but I think he
got really hurt this time.

1092
01:01:16,540 --> 01:01:20,997
This program is about the participants
playing as either Love or Money Catchers.

1093
01:01:21,022 --> 01:01:23,622
- Right.
- So she played a great game.

1094
01:01:23,978 --> 01:01:26,120
- She succeeded.
- Agreed.

1095
01:01:27,283 --> 01:01:29,083
- Oh, it's Da-Na!
- Da-Na.

1096
01:01:29,268 --> 01:01:31,150
She's the one I'm most curious about.

1097
01:01:32,519 --> 01:01:34,193
Whose box is that?

1098
01:01:34,218 --> 01:01:36,599
(This is the box of the one
who didn't get chosen by Da-Na.)

1099
01:01:36,624 --> 01:01:41,840
(Is it Ji-min? Or Won-jae?)

1100
01:01:43,490 --> 01:01:46,085
- Why does she suddenly
seem like a Love Catcher? - I know.

1101
01:01:46,360 --> 01:01:47,642
I suddenly feel that way, too.

1102
01:01:47,996 --> 01:01:51,226
I want to know who Da-Na will choose,
and I'm curious about the men's identities.

1103
01:01:51,251 --> 01:01:52,839
I'm dying to find out about Ji-min.

1104
01:01:52,864 --> 01:01:55,413
Were his tears fake or real?

1105
01:01:57,030 --> 01:01:59,907
(Her final selection)

1106
01:02:01,446 --> 01:02:04,646
- Are one of them Money?
- Are they both Money?

1107
01:02:04,671 --> 01:02:08,458
(The closer she gets, the
heavier her footsteps become.)

1108
01:02:09,885 --> 01:02:12,978
(She will go to...)

1109
01:02:13,003 --> 01:02:14,003
Who will she go to?

1110
01:02:17,646 --> 01:02:20,248
- Ji-min?
- Ji-min? Will she go to him?

1111
01:02:20,631 --> 01:02:24,649
(Or will she go to Won-jae, the
one who always looked at her?)

1112
01:02:24,674 --> 01:02:27,702
They both assured her of their feelings.

1113
01:02:27,727 --> 01:02:29,839
- That's right.
- They really did that.

1114
01:02:29,864 --> 01:02:32,603
They even told her that they
don't care if she's a Money Catcher.

1115
01:02:36,164 --> 01:02:37,564
She's passing by him.

1116
01:02:38,890 --> 01:02:40,993
Oh dear. This is crazy.

1117
01:02:42,061 --> 01:02:43,838
Oh no. Poor Ji-min.

1118
01:02:43,870 --> 01:02:46,713
(In the end, Ji-min wasn't chosen.)

1119
01:02:48,106 --> 01:02:50,043
Oh no. What's happening?

1120
01:02:50,068 --> 01:02:51,592
(Then she'll pick Won-jae, right?)

1121
01:02:52,020 --> 01:02:55,020
(Da-Na passes by Ji-min
and goes to Won-jae.)

1122
01:02:55,670 --> 01:02:56,737
Look at Won-jae.

1123
01:02:56,762 --> 01:02:58,289
(Smile)

1124
01:03:00,433 --> 01:03:05,644
(Jung Da-Na has chosen Kang Won-jae.)

1125
01:03:05,669 --> 01:03:07,822
Seriously, there are so many twists.

1126
01:03:09,050 --> 01:03:12,046
Ji-min and Da-Na looked so good together.

1127
01:03:13,570 --> 01:03:15,300
You really don't know until the end.

1128
01:03:15,325 --> 01:03:16,325
Wow, seriously.

1129
01:03:18,700 --> 01:03:21,512
- What's wrong with her expression?
- Why do you look so down?

1130
01:03:23,422 --> 01:03:25,144
I'll give you advice about your problems.

1131
01:03:26,850 --> 01:03:27,850
Sounds good.

1132
01:03:28,841 --> 01:03:32,325
- But why advice?
- She's saying she'll keep seeing him!

1133
01:03:32,350 --> 01:03:33,439
I see.

1134
01:03:33,464 --> 01:03:35,459
She's saying they should
get to know each other

1135
01:03:35,484 --> 01:03:37,354
slowly since she
observes people for a while.

1136
01:03:38,582 --> 01:03:40,675
(Finally, they exchange
their identity boxes.)

1137
01:03:40,700 --> 01:03:41,821
They must be so nervous.

1138
01:03:41,846 --> 01:03:43,376
Please both be Love Catchers.

1139
01:03:43,401 --> 01:03:44,401
What will they be?

1140
01:03:44,736 --> 01:03:46,657
There needs to be at least on Love Catcher.

1141
01:03:46,682 --> 01:03:49,438
(Now it's time to check
each other's identities.)

1142
01:03:49,463 --> 01:03:51,719
- Won-jae looks so...
- He's on cloud nine.

1143
01:03:53,031 --> 01:03:54,690
Please reveal your identities.

1144
01:03:56,393 --> 01:03:59,385
- I'm going to open it.
- Hang on.

1145
01:03:59,417 --> 01:04:00,769
What? Why?

1146
01:04:00,794 --> 01:04:02,666
(Why are you making me nervous?)

1147
01:04:02,691 --> 01:04:04,773
- Oh no!
- I hope they become a couple.

1148
01:04:04,798 --> 01:04:06,487
Yes, I hope they're both Love Catchers.

1149
01:04:07,810 --> 01:04:10,588
(What is Won-jae's identity?)

1150
01:04:10,613 --> 01:04:12,821
I hope Won-jae can be happy.

1151
01:04:13,658 --> 01:04:16,038
- I don't think I can check this.
- Why not?

1152
01:04:16,063 --> 01:04:17,263
- Huh?
- Why not?

1153
01:04:18,369 --> 01:04:20,543
- Why not?
- He must be nervous.

1154
01:04:21,395 --> 01:04:24,110
(Da-Na is holding Won-jae's identity box.)

1155
01:04:24,431 --> 01:04:25,698
Whatever you are...

1156
01:04:28,327 --> 01:04:29,327
I'm okay.

1157
01:04:30,333 --> 01:04:31,936
- Da-Na must be Love.
- Yeah.

1158
01:04:32,232 --> 01:04:33,299
This is awesome!

1159
01:04:34,076 --> 01:04:36,147
I think they're both Love Catchers.

1160
01:04:37,341 --> 01:04:38,674
Should we check now?

1161
01:04:39,352 --> 01:04:41,264
I hope they're both Love Catchers.

1162
01:04:41,289 --> 01:04:46,195
(Da-Na checks Won-jae's identity first.)

1163
01:04:49,556 --> 01:04:52,679
(She carefully opens his box.)

1164
01:04:53,382 --> 01:04:54,382
Please!

1165
01:04:56,450 --> 01:04:59,540
(After she checks it, her
expression looks kind of complicated.)

1166
01:04:59,565 --> 01:05:02,216
(And Won-jae gazes at her.)

1167
01:05:02,861 --> 01:05:04,328
- What?
- What is it?

1168
01:05:05,714 --> 01:05:07,412
He's not a Money Catcher, is he?

1169
01:05:11,394 --> 01:05:14,911
(Kang Won-jae = Love Catcher)

1170
01:05:15,289 --> 01:05:16,946
(Scared to death)

1171
01:05:17,090 --> 01:05:19,528
- I'm sorry! I doubted you!
- If he was a Money Catcher...

1172
01:05:19,560 --> 01:05:21,355
I almost got a heart attack!

1173
01:05:22,012 --> 01:05:25,056
(His pure love towards Da-Na was real.)

1174
01:05:25,081 --> 01:05:26,870
I feel like my health is worsening.

1175
01:05:30,971 --> 01:05:32,504
Please don't, Da-Na.

1176
01:05:32,965 --> 01:05:35,625
Don't frown. You're making me uneasy.

1177
01:05:37,581 --> 01:05:42,390
(What is Da-na's identity?)

1178
01:05:43,743 --> 01:05:46,301
(Love? Or Money?)

1179
01:05:48,441 --> 01:05:50,162
- He opened it.
- He saw it.

1180
01:05:50,187 --> 01:05:51,187
He has to smile.

1181
01:05:53,305 --> 01:05:55,273
- Don't tell me.
- Why did he close it?

1182
01:05:55,298 --> 01:05:58,608
(Her identity is...)

1183
01:05:59,589 --> 01:06:01,088
But I'm still grateful.

1184
01:06:01,358 --> 01:06:02,358
Is she Love?

1185
01:06:04,903 --> 01:06:05,903
I mean it.

1186
01:06:07,525 --> 01:06:09,341
Why is Da-Na so upset?

1187
01:06:10,611 --> 01:06:13,728
(Da-na's identity is finally revealed.)

1188
01:06:17,727 --> 01:06:19,449
(Please be a Love Catcher!)

1189
01:06:19,474 --> 01:06:20,541
I'm begging you!

1190
01:06:21,585 --> 01:06:25,785
(Jung Da-Na = Money Catcher)

1191
01:06:25,810 --> 01:06:27,610
- Oh goodness.
- Whatever!

1192
01:06:28,294 --> 01:06:30,111
(Someone save her!)

1193
01:06:30,136 --> 01:06:32,232
(Speechless 1/Speechless 2)

1194
01:06:32,322 --> 01:06:34,560
This is a horror program.

1195
01:06:34,585 --> 01:06:36,690
But this is what this program is about.

1196
01:06:36,715 --> 01:06:38,565
I'm sorry. I was too immersed in it.

1197
01:06:38,590 --> 01:06:40,678
Wow, but this is so shocking.

1198
01:06:41,169 --> 01:06:44,467
(The one Won-jae picked
is a Money Catcher.)

1199
01:06:44,803 --> 01:06:46,817
- I'm sorry...
- Oh dear.

1200
01:06:46,842 --> 01:06:48,308
I told you, it's okay.

1201
01:06:49,038 --> 01:06:51,410
I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

1202
01:06:52,327 --> 01:06:54,700
I'm actually really grateful
that you kept your promise.

1203
01:06:54,725 --> 01:06:57,216
- I'm sorry.
- I'm truly thankful.

1204
01:06:58,809 --> 01:07:04,637
(She can't stop crying
because of his sincerity.)

1205
01:07:05,245 --> 01:07:07,023
Don't cry. Why are you crying?

1206
01:07:09,078 --> 01:07:11,606
(Da-Na can't bring herself to look at him.)

1207
01:07:12,170 --> 01:07:14,331
You're pretty when you smile.
Smile for me.

1208
01:07:14,780 --> 01:07:17,049
(We want to cry!)

1209
01:07:17,702 --> 01:07:18,927
Don't be like that.

1210
01:07:18,952 --> 01:07:21,300
- I want to send a DM to Won-jae!
- Seriously!

1211
01:07:21,333 --> 01:07:25,177
- I want to tell him to cheer up!
- Can we do a video message for him?

1212
01:07:25,202 --> 01:07:28,283
Goodness, he's trying not to make
her feel uncomfortable until the end.

1213
01:07:28,667 --> 01:07:31,400
But I think he'll struggle for a long time.

1214
01:07:31,827 --> 01:07:32,827
Bye.

1215
01:07:34,697 --> 01:07:37,793
(Eventually, Da-Na leaves
Won-jae and walks away.)

1216
01:07:37,818 --> 01:07:41,558
- This is so sad.
- This is really pitiful.

1217
01:07:41,583 --> 01:07:45,299
(Won-jae showed his
pure love until she left.)

1218
01:07:51,253 --> 01:07:52,889
This is what you
call "pure love," right?

1219
01:07:52,914 --> 01:07:55,247
- Seriously.
- Won-jae is so amazing.

1220
01:07:55,272 --> 01:07:57,513
He gave her his whole
heart in just seven days?

1221
01:07:57,538 --> 01:07:59,471
He's cool until the very end.

1222
01:08:00,994 --> 01:08:03,763
(There's another person who
didn't get picked by anyone.)

1223
01:08:03,788 --> 01:08:05,276
- Ji-min.
- He's smiling.

1224
01:08:05,301 --> 01:08:08,166
Ji-min is laughing in disbelief, right?

1225
01:08:08,191 --> 01:08:09,567
His eyes look sad though.

1226
01:08:10,799 --> 01:08:12,569
- I'm curious.
- Is he Money?

1227
01:08:12,594 --> 01:08:14,794
- He's a Money Catcher.
- Is he?

1228
01:08:15,352 --> 01:08:16,352
Money.

1229
01:08:18,338 --> 01:08:22,247
(Ji-min = Love Catcher)

1230
01:08:23,956 --> 01:08:25,480
He was a Love Catcher?

1231
01:08:25,505 --> 01:08:27,870
Ahn Ji-min was Love!

1232
01:08:29,350 --> 01:08:35,168
Those tears were genuine.

1233
01:08:35,193 --> 01:08:38,119
I want to send him a
message saying that I'm sorry!

1234
01:08:38,143 --> 01:08:40,335
He was a sincere person.

1235
01:08:40,779 --> 01:08:42,449
(One more coin!)

1236
01:08:42,474 --> 01:08:46,898
The most unfortunate thing was that
there were no Love Catcher couples.

1237
01:08:46,923 --> 01:08:49,496
- I'm so sad!
- This is really upsetting.

1238
01:08:49,521 --> 01:08:50,654
It's unfortunate.

1239
01:08:51,677 --> 01:08:52,677
(Final Results)

1240
01:08:52,702 --> 01:08:56,154
(Love Catchers: Won-jae,
Ji-min, and Su-won)

1241
01:08:56,179 --> 01:09:01,484
(Money Catchers: Jae-hyung,
Yeo-min, In-seong, Ha-neul, and Da-Na)

1242
01:09:03,414 --> 01:09:10,198
(Money Catchers: Da-Na & Ha-neul
Prize: $50,000)

1243
01:09:10,719 --> 01:09:12,829
(Amazing!)

1244
01:09:12,854 --> 01:09:16,825
Da-Na and Ha-neul won
the prize money of $50,000.

1245
01:09:17,139 --> 01:09:18,536
(Congratulations!)

1246
01:09:18,561 --> 01:09:22,220
Wow, it's shocking that no
one had changed their identities.

1247
01:09:22,245 --> 01:09:27,703
I expected some twists, but they
were so shocking that I'm dizzy.

1248
01:09:28,293 --> 01:09:29,690
How many did you get?

1249
01:09:29,715 --> 01:09:32,405
- I have four.
- Me, too.

1250
01:09:33,211 --> 01:09:34,211
They're tied.

1251
01:09:34,538 --> 01:09:35,879
What happens now?

1252
01:09:35,904 --> 01:09:37,874
What about that mini event?

1253
01:09:38,138 --> 01:09:40,860
If you're a Money Catcher,
choose me to be safe, okay?

1254
01:09:41,641 --> 01:09:46,343
I thought Ji-min was a Money Catcher.

1255
01:09:46,368 --> 01:09:48,971
Or maybe he said that
'cause he's a Money Catcher,

1256
01:09:48,996 --> 01:09:51,751
and he's saying choose
her so that she won't feel bad.

1257
01:09:51,776 --> 01:09:53,699
No, no, no. That's impossible.

1258
01:09:53,724 --> 01:09:56,282
- You don't say? How much you wanna bet?
- One coin!

1259
01:09:56,307 --> 01:09:57,957
Then I'll bet a coin, too.

1260
01:09:57,982 --> 01:09:59,904
(They had a mini event
where they bet coins.)

1261
01:10:00,216 --> 01:10:02,483
Ho-jun, you can't forget this!

1262
01:10:03,372 --> 01:10:05,703
(Since he won the mini
event, he got one coin.)

1263
01:10:07,199 --> 01:10:09,206
To Son Ho-jun, who got first place,

1264
01:10:10,230 --> 01:10:12,697
- I shall present him with a gold coin.
- Congratulations!

1265
01:10:13,082 --> 01:10:15,086
(Thanks to Do-yeon, he got the gold coin.)

1266
01:10:15,111 --> 01:10:17,178
Do-yeon, you're last place now.

1267
01:10:18,410 --> 01:10:19,543
I became a loser.

1268
01:10:20,230 --> 01:10:24,548
I shall accept that and live with
an apologetic heart towards Ji-min.

1269
01:10:24,573 --> 01:10:26,448
- Sounds good.
- The inference game is over.

1270
01:10:27,363 --> 01:10:28,363
How was it?

1271
01:10:28,388 --> 01:10:30,892
It was so much fun, and
I know this is just a game,

1272
01:10:30,917 --> 01:10:32,891
but I learned you
shouldn't trust people easily.

1273
01:10:33,764 --> 01:10:35,964
- Correct.
- I learned a lesson.

1274
01:10:36,359 --> 01:10:39,874
I also realized you shouldn't
grow weak at the sight of tears.

1275
01:10:39,899 --> 01:10:40,899
That's true.

1276
01:10:40,924 --> 01:10:44,239
It was so enjoyable, and
each and every one of them

1277
01:10:44,264 --> 01:10:47,706
was so charming that I
want to meet them in real life.

1278
01:10:47,731 --> 01:10:48,731
Right!

1279
01:10:49,269 --> 01:10:54,921
Then I'll sell this gold coin
and use it to pay for our dinner.

1280
01:10:55,140 --> 01:10:56,727
(Let's go party!)

1281
01:10:56,752 --> 01:10:59,141
I guess we're going to
Clam Gangster Lab then.

1282
01:10:59,166 --> 01:11:00,270
C.G.L.!

1283
01:11:00,950 --> 01:11:03,551
(Thank you for loving
"Love Catcher in Seoul.")

1284
01:11:04,416 --> 01:11:07,624
(After the final selection ended,)

1285
01:11:07,649 --> 01:11:10,122
(everyone's identities were revealed.)

1286
01:11:10,147 --> 01:11:12,655
(Revealing the Identities)

1287
01:11:14,947 --> 01:11:18,873
(Lee Ha-neul = Money Catcher)

1288
01:11:21,717 --> 01:11:24,414
(Jung Da-Na = Money Catcher)

1289
01:11:39,613 --> 01:11:42,393
(Ahn Ji-min = Love Catcher)

1290
01:11:47,616 --> 01:11:49,719
(Ahn Ji-min = Love Catcher)

1291
01:12:10,631 --> 01:12:17,712
(Will you choose LOVE?
Or will you choose MONEY?)
